Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:25.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,翻译/时间轴：CharlesChouBlues\N转制请保留译者信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Our father,who art in heaven,\N我们在天上的父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,hallowed be thy name.\N愿人都尊你的名为圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.31,0:00:49.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thy kingdom come,\N愿你的国降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.48,0:00:54.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,thy will be done on earth as it is in heaven.\N愿你的旨意行在地上 如同行在天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Give us this day our daily bread,\N赐给我们日用的饮食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and forgive us our trespasses,\N赦免我们的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.66,0:01:06.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,as we forgive those who trespass against us.\N如同我们免了人的债
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Lead us not into temptation,\N不教我们遇见试探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but deliver us from evil.\N救我们脱离凶恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.27,0:01:18.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,For the kingdom,the power,and the glory are yours,\N因为国度 权柄 荣耀 全都属于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.37,0:01:21.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,now and forever.\N直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Amen.\N阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.73,0:01:43.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Looking at mostly cloudy skies</i>\N大部地区都将继续维持多云天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>and with lows in the upper 20s.</i>\N最低气温华氏20度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>There will likely be some refreeze on some of the roads.</i>\N部分路面可能会再次结冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.60,0:01:51.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>So,slick spots are possible tonight in isolated lo...</i>\N因此今晚个别偏远地区将出现路面打滑的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You know the most important thing\N知道你爷爷教会我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,your granddad ever taught me?\N最重要的事情是什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready.\N时刻做好准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.79,0:02:09.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane,flood,whatever it ends up being.\N飓风 洪水 无论遇到什么灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No more food gets delivered to the grocery store,\N哪怕食品店断货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,gas stations dry up.\N储油池见底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,People just turn on each other,and,uh...\N人们彼此拔刀相向 或者...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden,\N其它突发情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:23.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,all that stands between you and being dead is you.\N你都必须明白 唯有自救 才能生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of you,son.\N我为你感到骄傲 儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.51,0:02:34.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It was a nice shot.\N那一枪打得漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.76,0:02:51.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Put your hand in the hand of the man who stilled the water</i>\N<i>牵着他为你遮风挡雨的手</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:58.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>put your hand in the hand of the man who calmed the sea</i>\N<i>牵着他让波涛止息的手</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>take a look at yourself</i>\N<i>看看如镜水面上映出的你</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.28,0:03:05.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>and you can look at others differently</i>\N<i>想想众生在这世上都是唯一</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>By putting your hand in the hand</i>\N<i>你只要牵着他的手</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:13.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>of the man from galilee</i>\N<i>这男人来自加利利</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.39,0:03:19.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>every time I look at the holy book,I want to tremble</i>\N<i>每当我看见圣经 便不由感激颤抖</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>and then I read about the part</i>\N<i>每当我读到</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>where a carpenter cleared the temple...</i>\N<i>那木工清扫寺庙...</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,come on,hon.\N快点  宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait,wait,wait. I forgot something.\N等等 等一下 我忘了东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second,Anna!\N等我一下 安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.74,0:03:36.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ralph,you have the venison?\N拉尔夫 你拿上鹿肉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.\N拿了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the pie.\N我把派给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Are we taking the truck?\N我们要坐小卡车去么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We're going up the street,you dope.\N我们就到街对面 小傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:55.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,wait for your mother,please.\N嘿 等等妈妈.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a ride.\N我要骑大马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Here.\N来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:02.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,you're gettin' heavy.\N噢 你真是越来越重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Um,Danny's dad said he'd sell me their old car.\N丹尼的爸爸说他要把他的旧车卖给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I got half of what I need saved from the summer.\N今年夏天我已经存够一半钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- I thought maybe you'd...- forget it.\N- 我在想你能不能.... - 别想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely get enough carpentry work\N现在的木工活太难接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,to keep up with the mortgage.\N就目前的状况看连还房贷都成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,why don't you rent out grandpa's old apartment house?\N为什么不把爷爷的老房子租出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Like I keep telling your mother,it's an old building,\N我不是一直和你妈说那房子太旧了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll cost a fortune to fix it up.\N要修好它也得花一大笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,okay.\N来了来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!\N他们来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.\N你好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Thanksgiving. Happy Thanksgiving.\N- 感恩节快乐!  - 感恩节快乐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna,wait until we're invited.\N安娜 要等人家邀请你才可以进去,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,for God's sake,Keller.Get the hell in here.\N看在上帝的份上 凯勒 快点进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Aah!\N啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keller,you got the deer you shot?\N凯勒 这鹿是你打来的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This one's Ralph's.\N这头是拉尔夫打的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,you killed it,you take it into the kitchen.\N既然是你打的 你就负责把它拿进厨房去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thank you.\N- 好的. - 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Thanksgiving.\N感恩节快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Happy Thanksgiving. - There he is.\N- 感恩节快乐. - 他在这儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Happy t-day.\N谢谢.感恩节快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right.Joy. Joy,three times.\N好了 乔伊 乔伊 都跟你说过三次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy,get your dolls off the table.Y'all missing the game.\N- 乔伊 把你的娃娃们从桌上拿走 - 你们都错过游戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Anna! Anna! - Hi. How are you?\N- 安娜 安娜! - 嗨 你好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Happy Thanksgiving.\N嘿 . 感恩节快乐.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna,come here.\N安娜 过来这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We wait until we're invited.You understand?\N我们要先得到别人的邀请才可以进去 懂了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge of this.\N你来弄这个吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Us veterinarians make lousy butchers.\N我们兽医切起肉来还真不在行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.\N没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go outside with joy?\N我可以和乔伊去外边玩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,convince your brother to go with you,and you can.\N你能拉上你哥哥陪你一起去就行.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And wear a hat,please.\N记得戴上帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're just getting over a cold.\N你感冒才刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy,you wear a hat,too.\N乔伊 你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.30,0:05:45.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you feel bad for that deer\N你打死那头鹿的时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when you shot it?\N是不是觉得有点难过？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel bad for cows when you go into McDonald's?\N你去麦当劳的时候也为那些牛感到难过么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's... that's what my dad says.\N我爸就是那么跟我说的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And the deer,if they have too many babies,\N说到鹿嘛 如果它们生了太多小鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,then the babies starve anyway.\N那些小鹿最后也会饿死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta keep the population down.\N所以你需要控制种群的数量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Your dad say that,too?\N也对 这也是你爸和你说的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Pull harder.\N用力拉.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,hey! Get away from that thing!\N嘿 嘿! 离那辆车远一点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see that.\N让我来试试.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,let's go.\N快点 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I said let's go! \N我说了 我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.53,0:06:14.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. You can't just take somebody's stuff like that.\N下来 你不能随便碰别人的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let's go!\N不能上去 我们走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on,come on,come on.\N听话 听话 快下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Shh.You hear that?\N等等 嘘..你听到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's in there.\N有人在里面.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,I don't feel like getting yelled at.\N这下好了 我可不想被车主骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:28.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Not on Thanksgiving,okay?\N我们走吧 感恩节的时候别惹事 知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now the school board's telling me\N现在 学校董事会告诉我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,there's no money for new marching-band uniforms.\N他们没钱给军乐队买新制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,These kids are wearin' the same uniforms\N我们去那里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,they had when we went there,and they were old then.\N那些孩子们还穿着原来的旧制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,marchin' right out of 1979.\N和1979年那会一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he speaking to me?\N为什么它不跟我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't speak.\N它不会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Cutie pie.\N可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.\N嗯嗯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my gosh!\N喔 天哪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast,too.\N它跑得可快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's so quick.\NIs that a slide?\N太快了 那是个滑梯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you,all. Thank you,all. Got a surprise.\N谢谢大家 我要给你们个惊喜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I am taking requests.\N我可以给你们来一个『听众点播』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! No.\N- 好! - 别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta listen out for it,'cause this is not easy.\N你们都得好好听听 这可不是件容易事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mom. Mommy,can I take joy to our house?\N妈妈 我可以带乔伊去我们家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N为什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My red whistle.She's gonna help me look for it.\N她要去帮我找我的红口哨.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my sweetheart,I think that red whistle is long gone.\N噢 宝贝 那个口哨早就不见了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What whistle?\N什么口哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency whistle daddy gave me.\N是我爸爸给我的求救口哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it...\N被我弄丢了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:37.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,133 days ago.\N...大约133天以前.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,if you want to find a whistle,\N好吧 如果你想找到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you have to whistle for it.\N得也得先吹几声口哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll do "jingle bells" to find it.\N所以 我们先来表演一首『铃儿响叮当』吧 好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.63,0:07:52.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Jingle bells,Batman smells,Robin laid an egg</i>\N<i>叮叮当 蝙蝠侠香 罗宾下蛋黄</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:57.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>the Batmobile lost its wheels,and joker got away... hey!</i>\N<i>蝙蝠车子轮胎掉 小丑逃跑了 嘿！</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Okay! Okay! You can go,all right?\N很棒 好了 好了! 你们可以走咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure Eliza and Ralph go with you,please.\N不过要让伊莱札和拉尔夫陪你们一起去.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- No looking in the basement. - I won't.\N- 别去地下室. - 我不会的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all eardrums are just startin' to grow.\N你们要小心你们的鼓膜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to damage them yet.\N我可不想把它们震坏了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I am taking requests from you,Keller.\N你可以点播一首 凯勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,From me?\N我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Your day,your request.\N这是你的日子 所以你先来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Uh,the piano.\N噢 那就钢琴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,no,no. So all set?\N不不不不..... 你们都准备好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait,listen,he used to love...\N等一下 听我说 他以前特喜欢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he used to dresslike <i>Springsteen.</i>\N他整天打扮得跟斯普林斯汀一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Really? - I still love Springsteen.\N- 真的吗?   - 我现在还很喜欢斯普林斯汀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,"The River," "Jersey Girl."\N『河流』 『泽西女孩』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,I ain't white,and I like him too much\N这个嘛 我不是白人 但是我爱死他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm too drunk to cover the Boss.\N不过我现在喝得太多了 没法吹Boss的曲子\N（注：Boss是乐迷给Bruce Springsteen起的绰号）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Honey? What else?\N亲爱的 还有什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing comes to mind. Nothing.\N别问我 我脑袋里一片空白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,I know. What?\N- 噢 我想起来了 - 什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He actually loves "the star-spangled banner."\N他还喜欢『星条旗永不落』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.81,0:08:40.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Sings it in the shower.\N洗澡的时候都会唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.\N没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes,you do! - I got you.\N- 怎么没有了！ - 我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your sisters?\N妹妹们上哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find them.\N我找不到她们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You,uh,you go to the house with them?\N你没有跟她们一起回家?？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. What are you talking about?\N没有啊 什么一起回家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier? No.\N- 早些时候没有? - 没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What? They were supposed to come down earlier and get you.\N什么？她们之前不是说要下来找你们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't come get you?\N她们没来找你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. We haven't seen them since we ate.\N没有 吃过晚饭后就没再见过她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. All right.\N没事 先别急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:38.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably at our house.\N她们可能还在我们家。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna? Joy?\N安娜? 乔伊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Girls?\N孩子们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Girls?!\N孩子们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Who put these dishes in here?\N是谁把那些盘子扔到这里的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here.They weren't outside.\N- 出去吧 - 她们没在外边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to rain.\N外边开始下雨了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check over by Maria's swing?\N你有没有去玛丽娅家的秋千那里看过?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,they're gettin' whupped when they get here.\N等她们回来可得好好教训教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,Grace.I whup kids.\N抱歉 格蕾丝 我得教训下她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So they weren't there either?\N她们也不在那边?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They must be at home.\N她们肯定在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Are they here?\N她们在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. They're not here.They weren't there?\N- 不在 - 她们也没在那边?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,they're not at our house.\N没有 她们不在我们家.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,they're not there.\N她们没在那边.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I checked the entire house.They're not here.\N我把整个房子都找遍了 都没见着她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The... the...the RV.\N那辆...那辆小房车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What RV?\N什么小房车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Dad,there was this RV,and they were playing on it.\N爸 之前那里停了一辆房车 她们爬上去玩来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We thought there was someone inside.\N我们觉得车里好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where was it? Show me.\N哪里？车在哪里？指给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here.\N你在这里等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna gonna over the house again.\N我在房子里再找找看.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. Relax.\N别急 别急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go that way. I'll meet you on the other side.\N你去那边 我们分开走 到那边会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?!\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy!\N乔伊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Roger,you seen my daughter walk by here?\N罗杰 有没有看到我女儿经过这边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. Is there a problem?\N没看到 出什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Here!\N就是这里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Dad,it was parked right here.\N爸 那辆车当时就停在这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna? Anna?\N安娜? 安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello,hello!\N有人吗? 有人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see 'em? No!\N- 你看到她们了吗? - 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!\N有人吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find 'em!\N我找不到她们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Were you messing around in this house? - No.\N- 你们是不是在这捣乱来着  - 没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to come here. We weren't.\N- 跟你说过不要来这里 - 又不是我们要来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They were just on the RV,and we got them off of it.\N当时她们在那辆房车上玩 我们过来只是要把她们抱下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything you remember about that rv.\N好好想想那辆房车长什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Everything. A-a ladder on the back.\N- 仔细想想 - 车后有个梯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Police,police.\N报警 报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Thanksgiving.\N感恩节快乐.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.\N谢谢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,you have any of those,um,fortune-cookie things?\N嘿 你们这里有没有卖...那种幸运饼干？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:12.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My boss told me cops don't like fortune cookies.\N我老板说警察不喜欢幸运饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What year were you born?\N你是属什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a dragon or a snake or a horse?\N龙？或者蛇？还是马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a monkey.\N我属猴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,you're a monkey.\N噢,你是属猴子的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're very intelligent.\N你非常聪明.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You have an ability to influence people.\N拥有某种可以影响他人的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Think maybe you could influence your boss\N也许你可以试着去影响下你的老板...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,to lower the check a little bit?\N少收我一点钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. I cannot.\N这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My boss is a rooster.\N我老板是属鸡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Silly,selfish,and eccentric.\N属鸡的人：愚蠢 自私 古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's...\N这是有点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All units,all units,\N各小队请注意 各小队请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.47,0:12:55.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,an RV was reported matching the description.\N发现符合描述的小型房车一辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The vehicle is parked at a rest stop off of route 46,\N该车辆目前正停靠46号公路外的一个休息站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,northbound,past exit 17.\N位于第17出口北外侧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Any available units?\N是否有巡逻车辆在目标区域附近？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is 12-12 responding.\N警员12-12 响应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,10-80 responding.\N警员10-80 响应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is 13-40.I'm five minutes out.\N这里是警员13-40 距目标5分钟路程.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.42,0:13:11.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet the responding units.\N我现在过去与小队汇合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,12-12 standing by.\N12-12 收到待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,10-80 standing by.\N10-80 收到待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,13-40. I'm on scene.\N13-40 到达现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Be advised,we're moving in.\N小队注意 准备包抄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hey,don't move! Hey!\N喂 别跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa,whoa,watch out!\N小心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,don't shoot!\N别开枪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!\N别开枪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!\N别开枪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,Sloan,take the right!\N好了 斯隆 你去右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Clear!\N安全!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Clear!\N安全!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait,wait,wait,wait,wait! I got this.\N好 等等 等一下 让我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that.\N把那个给我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I see you in there.\N我看到你了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me both your hands right now.\N把两只手举起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,I see you in there!\N我看到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your hands!\N把手举起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands right now!\N两只手！快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.Slow. Slow. Slow!\N对 就这样 慢一点！慢一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Slow. Slowly. Both hands.\N慢一点 两只手.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.90,0:15:45.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Both fuckin' hands!\N我他妈说了两只手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Walk! Walk!\N走 快走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.31,0:15:52.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N嘿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Walk!\N快走!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Get up!\N站起来!起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!\N起来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me those girls!\N孩子们呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me where you put those girls,huh?\N你把那些女孩藏在什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those girls?\N女孩们在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those girls?!\N女孩们在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,give me the flashlight.Sir.\N警官 把手电筒给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me where those girls...they in the woods?\N孩子们在哪里？在树林里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You put them in the woods?\N你把她们带进树林了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.17,0:16:18.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you put those girls?\N你把那些女孩藏在什么地方了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.07,0:16:21.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?!\N你听见我说话了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck is this guy on?\N这家伙他妈的怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's high on something.\N他可能是嗑药了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put this fucking guy in the car.\N把他给我弄到车里去.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get him in the car. Put him in the fucking car!\N- 把他弄上车去 - 快把他弄上车!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Walk! Let's go.\N- 快走! - 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,call PSP,tell 'em to send their scent dogs.\N给局里打个电话 把警犬带过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And seal off the whole area.\N封锁整个区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance,all of it.\N包括这条公路所有的出入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right.\N收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You,come with me.\N你 跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,they weren't playing on your RV?\N她们没有在你的房车上玩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,take a look at 'em again.\N好 再看看她们的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't recognize these girls?\N你不认得这两个女孩 ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see them.May I sit down?\N我从没见过她们,我可以坐下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do in the RV? Answer my question.\N你在车里做什么? 回答我的问题.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep there.\N我在那里睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep in there?\N你在车里睡觉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You were sleeping out there?\N你说你在睡觉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,In the day?\N白天睡觉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the RV parked outside the house?\N为什么你的车会停在那座房子外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.\N嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I went for a drive?\N我去那边兜风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You went for a drive? You weren't driving.\N你去兜风?你不是把车子停在那里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know for a fact those girls were playing outside your rv.\N我知道就是那两个女孩在你的房车外头玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't driving.It was parked.\N你没有在开车 当时车是停着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a special day?\N是什么特殊的日子么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Were you planning on taking two little girls?\N你是不是早就计划好了要带走那两个小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done that before?\N你之前是不是也干过这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you ask them to come inside? - No.\N- 你有没有叫她们上车? - 没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You ask them to come inside the RV and then you take them away?\N是不是你叫她们上车玩 然后就把她们带走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you put those girls somewhere?\N你是不是把那两个小女孩藏起来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,May I sit down? Come on.\N- 我可以坐下吗? - 快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you put those girls somewhere? - Please don't touch me.\N- 你是不是把那两个小女孩藏起来了 - 不要碰我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you put those girls somewhere.\N我知道你把那两个小女孩藏在某个地方了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You hide 'em? No.\N- 你把她们藏起来了? - 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How did you hide 'em? Do you tie 'em up?\N你把她们藏在哪里? 你是不是把她们绑起来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you tie 'em up?\N你是不是把她们绑起来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.36,0:17:50.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey. Hey. Hey.\N嘿 嘿 嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I know you're a good guy,all right?\N听着 我知道你是个好人 好么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're a decent guy.\N我知道你是个老实人.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not tryin' to tell you you're doing anything bad.\N我的意思不是说你干了什么坏事.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just tryin' to get the right answers out of you,okay?\N我只是想要听你说实话 知道了么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The real ones. That's all I want.\N说实话就行. 只要实话.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you usually park your rv,Alex?\N你平时把房车停在哪 亚历克斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My aunt's house. Your aunt's house?\N- 在我姑妈家. - 你姑妈家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She lets me park it in the backyard.\N她让我把车子停在她的后院里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The grass don't grow back there anyway.\N反正后面也不会再长草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.56,0:18:17.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It was my husband's.\N那是我丈夫的车.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.26,0:18:20.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,For sale,if you want it.\N我打算卖了 你要吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,thanks.\N不 谢谢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,would you tell me\N噢 那能不能请你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,what you're doin' on my property then?\N你在我家院子里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.27,0:18:34.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad to know where he is.\N我总算知道他跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.41,0:18:38.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's always home before dark,and...\N他平时总在天黑前就回到家了 而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand.\N我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That boy has never been in trouble,\N那孩子以前从来没惹过麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,not a day in his life.\N一次都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.42,0:18:48.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,in the summertime,\N嗯,夏天的时候,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he sleeps out in the camper some,but...\N他会睡在外面的露营车里 不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.23,0:18:55.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This time of year,he sleeps in here on the sofa bed.\N每年这个时候 他会回沙发上睡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's my husband.\N那是我丈夫.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We had a fight,jeez,five years ago.\N我们五年前大吵了一架 啧啧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.35,0:19:15.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Walked out,didn't come back.\N他一气之下走了 再也没回来过.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.65,0:19:19.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex loved him like a father.\N亚历克斯很爱他 把他看作亲生父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Alex's real parents?\N亚历克斯的亲生父母呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My husband's brother and his girlfriend,\N他是我小叔子的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.13,0:19:31.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,they died in a car accident when Alex was about 6.\N亚历克斯六岁的时候 他和妻子出车祸死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to hear that.\N我很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have much.\N他也没什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What have you got?\N找到什么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,this thing's clean.\N里头一干二净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.89,0:19:57.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,it's filthy as shit,but we didn't find anything.\N我是说 虽然这车脏得像坨屎 不过我们什么线索都没找到.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:20:00.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't find any,uh,wool fibers,anything like that?\N什么都没发现？羊毛纤维之类的也没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The girls could be wearing some wool gloves or wool hat.\N那两个女孩好像戴着羊毛手套或者帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No cotton fibers?\N也没有发现棉纤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,if he was just usin' this thing to transport 'em,\N这个嘛 如果他只是用这车载了她们一程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I might buy that.\N没线索也不奇怪.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But if there had been a struggle,\N但如果她们在车上挣扎过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I would have found something.\N那我肯定会发现痕迹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'd start lookin' in the woods by the rest stop.\N我会去休息站那的树林里再找找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Half the uniformed cops in the state\N半个州的警力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,are doin' that right now.\N现在都给调去找人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done with this thing,\N等你检查完这车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,can you send a crew over to the aunt's house?\N可以派人去趟嫌疑人的姑妈家么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?!\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for comin'. Franklin birch.\N辛苦您了 我是富兰克林·伯奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My wife's in here.\N我妻子在屋里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Honey?\N亲爱的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Nancy.\N她叫南希.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.92,0:21:35.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Loki is...honey?\N洛奇警探是来...亲爱的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:46.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,These photos are better than the ones my husband gave you.\N这些照片比我丈夫给你的要好一些.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You can see her eyes more clearly.\N你可以更清楚地看到她的眼睛.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.76,0:22:18.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So,did we pass?\N我们通过了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.03,0:22:21.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,what did you say?\N不好意思 你刚说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The poly thing.\N测谎仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The lie detector we took this morning.\N今早做的测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did we pass?\N我们通过了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,yeah,yeah. Sorry.\N噢 那个啊 是的 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.78,0:22:33.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,we appreciate your cooperation.\N感谢你们的配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.48,0:22:39.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing,all the...all this fuss.\N实在是太尴尬了 所有的...所有这些破事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gonna think we're crazy\N不管她们藏在哪里 等她们玩腻了回来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.89,0:22:44.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when those two come out of hiding,wherever they are.\N所有的人肯定都会把我们当疯子看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.99,0:22:49.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some reason to believe they ran away?\N你觉得她们可能只是离家出走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're happy.\N她们很快乐.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.54,0:23:00.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They must have run away.\N对 她们肯定是离家出走了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I think they must have run away.\N我想她们是离家出走了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.01,0:23:04.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right?\N对吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.18,0:23:11.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Um,your police captain told me\N你们的局长告诉我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that you've solved every case that you've ever been assigned.\N凡是你接手的案子 你都可以查个水落石出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?\N是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.10,0:23:26.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\N对不起.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I am so sorry.\N我很抱歉.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.67,0:23:32.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... do you have children,detective?\N警探 你有孩子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.11,0:23:40.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna find your daughter.\N我会找到你女儿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.08,0:23:45.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that they came back here\N我们认为她们昨晚离开伯奇家后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,after they left you at the birches' yesterday.\N回来过这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.39,0:23:50.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They were looking for Anna's red whistle.\N她们在找安娜的红口哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.46,0:23:51.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right.\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.79,0:23:53.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I read your statement.\N我看过你的笔录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.86,0:23:57.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm detective Loki.\N我是洛奇警探.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.10,0:23:59.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading up the investigation\N我负责调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.57,0:24:02.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,into your daughter's disappearance.\N你女儿的失踪案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please sit down.\N请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.44,0:24:06.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,uh,m-my son already told you\N我儿子已经告诉过你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.94,0:24:10.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that the guy was inside the RV just watchin' 'em,right?\N那辆房车里的人在偷窥她们 是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.91,0:24:14.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found any physical evidence inside the RV.\N对 不过我们还没有在那辆车里找到任何物证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Or his aunt's house where he lives.\N他姑妈家的房子也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.48,0:24:19.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?\N什么都没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.75,0:24:22.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex Jones unfortunately has the I.Q. Of a 10-year-old.\N亚历克斯·琼斯的智商仅相当于一个10岁儿童
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.72,0:24:26.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that someone with the I.Q. Of a 10-year-old\N一个只有10岁智商的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.06,0:24:29.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,could abduct two girls in broad daylight and then...\N要在大白天绑架两个女孩 然后又让她们凭空消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.06,0:24:30.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow make them disappear.\N那几乎是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.90,0:24:34.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,well,how can he drive an rv?\N如果是那样 那他为什么会驾驶房车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.60,0:24:38.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't answer a question...\N我是说 如果他连问题都回答不了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.17,0:24:41.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,he has a legal Pennsylvania license.\N这个嘛 他确实有合法的宾州驾照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.14,0:24:44.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And he ran,right? They said he tried to run away.\N他试图逃跑对吗? 他们说他当时正准备逃跑.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.78,0:24:47.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why... why... Why would he run?\N为什么--为什么他要逃跑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.15,0:24:49.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I've just spent 10 hours questioning this boy. Okay?\N我刚花了10个小时审讯那个男孩 知道么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.98,0:24:51.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I hear what you're saying.\N你说的我都明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.42,0:24:56.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Did... did you give him a lie detector?\N那你会给他测谎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.12,0:24:58.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You gave us a lie detector. Did you give him one?\N你给我们都测过谎了 那你会给他测谎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.93,0:25:00.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sir,I understand what you're asking me. Yes,we did.\N先生 我知道你想问什么 是的 我们测过了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.86,0:25:03.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We gave him a lie detector,and there is no way of...\N我们给他测过谎了 结果显示他并没.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.53,0:25:06.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,A lie detector doesn't work\N如果一个人连问题都无法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.83,0:25:08.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't understand the questions.\N测谎仪能有什么用呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.54,0:25:10.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,maybe he wasn't on his own.\N那他可能有帮凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.17,0:25:11.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How could he drive an rv\N一个智商只有10岁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.51,0:25:12.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,if he has an I.Q. of a 10-year-old?\N要怎么驾驶一辆房车呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.97,0:25:14.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,we're considering all possibilities.\N我们要考虑到所有的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.88,0:25:17.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you are considering all possibilities.\N我不觉得你考虑到了所有的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.21,0:25:20.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I-I hear what you're saying. Sir... sir...you listen to me.\N- 我已经听到你说的话了 - 先生 先生你听我说.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.01,0:25:22.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut the fuck up for a fucking second!\N你他妈的能不能先闭上嘴听我把话说完！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.68,0:25:25.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm gonna need you to do for me.\N我需要你配合我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.69,0:25:27.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to calm down.\N你先冷静.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.12,0:25:30.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.\N对不起 我很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.79,0:25:32.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me for a second.\N请你听我把话说完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.69,0:25:35.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover,I understand this is an incredibly hard time.\N多佛先生 我明白现在对你来说一定很难熬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.70,0:25:38.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I have every uniformed police officer in this state\N但是现在整个州的警力都已经出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.17,0:25:39.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,looking for Anna.\N在寻找安娜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.63,0:25:42.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what any of this means.\N我不懂那是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.37,0:25:43.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They said he ran.\N他们说他试图逃跑.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.64,0:25:45.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They said he tried to get away.\N他们说他当时试图逃跑.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.74,0:25:48.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why he would try to run away.\N我不明白为什么他要逃跑.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.84,0:25:52.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We're considering all possibilities,Mr. Dover.\N我们会考虑所有的可能性 多佛先生.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.88,0:25:54.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I hear what you're saying.\N我已经听到你所说的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.72,0:25:57.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crossing anybody off my list.\N我不会漏掉任何人的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.49,0:26:01.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Let me do my job.\N剩下的就交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.20,0:26:15.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.87,0:26:18.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Detective!\N警探先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.44,0:26:20.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh,shit. - Hey!\N- 该死 - 喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.88,0:26:24.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He stays in custody until my daughter's found,right?\N在我女儿被找到之前 他会一直待在拘留所里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.25,0:26:26.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right?\N对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.55,0:26:27.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We have a 48-hour hold on him\N我们只能依法拘留他48小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.92,0:26:29.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that ends tomorrow unless we bring charges.\N除非提出指控 不然他明天就会被释放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.58,0:26:32.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,charge him with something. Charge him.\N那就起诉他,起诉他.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover,I understand what you're...\N多佛先生 我理解你的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.52,0:26:36.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,detective,detective,two little girls\N警探先生 警探先生 两个小女孩的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.56,0:26:38.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,have got to be worth whatever little rule\N还抵不过那些条条框框么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.69,0:26:41.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you've got to break to keep that asshole in custody.\N你必须想办法把那混蛋继续关着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.30,0:26:43.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now,I know you can't promise me anything.\N我明白你现在也不能跟我保证什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.46,0:26:44.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.\N我能理解.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.77,0:26:46.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm asking you to be 100% sure.\N我只是想请求你一定要谨慎行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.37,0:26:49.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.24,0:26:52.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.\N感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.24,0:26:56.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So you're positive he's innocent,\N所以说 尽管你已经确定他是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.14,0:26:57.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but you want to keep holding him?\N但你还想继续把他扣在这儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.75,0:26:59.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna Dover's father was on my ass this morning.\N安娜·多佛的父亲烦我一早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.81,0:27:02.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it. I understand. But it's not gonna happen.\N行了 我明白你的意思 可你知道那是不可能的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.12,0:27:04.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was asking for one more day. Fuck you.\N- 就再多关他一天而已 - 去你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.65,0:27:06.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,no.\N别傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.22,0:27:07.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You find his daughter,he'll forgive you.\N你找到他的女儿 他自然就会原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.82,0:27:09.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't,he's gonna hate you anyway.\N不然他就能恨你一辈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.39,0:27:11.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So what's next?\N接下来打算做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.79,0:27:13.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm knockin' on doors all night.\N整个晚上我都得去挨家挨户地敲门调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.56,0:27:16.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,well,you're comin' up on 24 hours missing,\N是啊 人不见都快24小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.06,0:27:18.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and you have exactly shit.\N你连个屁都还没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.23,0:27:19.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,I've got nine level-three sex offenders\N谁说的 我已经逮住九个三级强奸犯了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.97,0:27:21.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,living within a 10-mile radius of Fairmont circle.\N都住在费尔蒙特周围方圆10公里以内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.64,0:27:22.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So if you don't mind...\N所以 如果你不介意...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.90,0:27:23.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Then go. Yeah.\N- 行了 快走吧 - 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go.\N走吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.18,0:27:37.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here.\N就在这里..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.79,0:27:47.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I-I'm staying straight,okay?\N听着 我是个直男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.76,0:27:52.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,hey,look.Look,I know you're...\N嘿 听着 我知道你....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.20,0:27:55.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you like yourself some German porn,huh?\N你喜欢德国产的片子是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.47,0:27:58.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I was...\N听着 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.87,0:28:35.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Open up! It's the police!\N神父 快开门 警察！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.28,0:29:15.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Father!\N神父!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.02,0:29:22.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Father.\N神父.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.96,0:29:30.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You mind if I take a look around?\N你不介意我四处看看吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.62,0:29:57.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin'drunk.\N老酒鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.27,0:30:16.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck?\N这他妈的是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.68,0:30:22.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.\N哇.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.78,0:31:02.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Aye. Fuck.\N噢 操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.19,0:32:13.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Please,God! God!\N啊 求求你 啊 天哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.36,0:32:15.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of your buddy down there,huh?\N地下室里的那家伙是谁 啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.40,0:32:18.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name,huh? I don't know his name.\N- 叫什么名字？ - 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.13,0:32:19.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know his name?\N你不知道他的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.30,0:32:20.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his name.\N我不知道他的名字!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.57,0:32:22.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,you know what?\N你知道吗 神父...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.14,0:32:23.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I spent six years in Huntington Boys' Home,father.\N我曾经在亨廷顿男童院待过6年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.64,0:32:26.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You know the Huntington Boys' Home,right? Huh?\N你知道亨廷顿男童院 对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.21,0:32:27.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hurting a fuck like you'd be a real treat for me.\N我最喜欢教训你这样的老混蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.88,0:32:29.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me his fuckin' name?\N为什么你他妈不告诉我他的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.28,0:32:30.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't tell me his name.\N他没有告诉过我他的名字.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.71,0:32:34.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He came to me for confession.\N我来找我忏悔.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:34.08,0:32:37.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd killed 16 children.He bragged about it.\N他说他杀了16个小孩 用的是一种自豪的语气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.38,0:32:40.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I convinced him to come back here.\N我说服他回来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.42,0:32:42.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd kill more.\N因为他说他要杀更多孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.39,0:32:44.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,16 children,huh?\N16个小孩 是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.49,0:32:47.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go,you fucking chicken-hawk!\N跟我走 你这个该死的鸡奸犯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.13,0:33:21.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.36,0:33:22.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're letting him go.\N他们放人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.96,0:33:24.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What? The man.\N- 什么? - 那个男人.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.83,0:33:27.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The police said they're letting him go today.\N那些警察说他们今天放人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.87,0:33:30.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay.I'll take care of it.\N我知道了 我会处理的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.64,0:33:33.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Dad? Keep searching.\N- 爸爸? - 继续找.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.81,0:33:35.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you goin'?!\N你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.45,0:33:45.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to write your whole name.\N你要写你的全名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.46,0:33:52.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.\N这样就对了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.30,0:33:59.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm. Good job.\N嗯 很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.87,0:34:01.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now you give it to the man.\N现在把它交给那个人.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.98,0:34:12.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Come on.\N好了 我们走吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.58,0:34:18.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you minding these people out here.\N别搭理外面那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.19,0:34:20.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to them. You've got nothing to say to them. Come on.\N别跟他们讲话 你没话和他们说 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.67,0:34:38.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,Alex. You took those kids,didn't you?\N说说吧 亚历克斯 是你带走了那些孩子 是不是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.21,0:34:39.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...I just want to talk.\N- 先生... - 我只是想要跟他谈谈.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:39.87,0:34:41.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's a free man,I'm a free man!\N他是个自由人 我也是自由人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.58,0:34:46.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tell me what you did with them!\N告诉我你对她们做了什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.88,0:34:48.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!\N告诉我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.18,0:34:50.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't cry until I left them.\N我一走她们就开始哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.18,0:34:51.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? What did you say?!\N你刚说什么？你刚才说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.85,0:34:53.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa,no,no!\N噢 不不不不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.19,0:34:56.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin' get off!\N放开我！妈的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.62,0:34:58.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,God! Get up!\N天哪 快起来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.19,0:35:00.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get him down! Get him down!\N按住他！按住他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.56,0:35:02.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Move back!\N后退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.13,0:35:04.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please,just let us go.\N拜托了 让我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.87,0:35:07.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine. Thank you.\N我们没事 谢谢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.47,0:35:16.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now,I know your dad was a guard at Graterford.\N我知道你爸爸曾经是格雷特福德监狱的守卫.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.38,0:35:19.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got a daughter of my own,\N我也有个女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.31,0:35:22.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,so we're gonna pretend this never happened.\N所以 我们就假装什么都没发生过.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.92,0:35:24.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And as for Alex Jones,\N至于亚历克斯·琼斯,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.72,0:35:27.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he has orders not to leave the commonwealth.\N我们暂时会限制他出境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.49,0:35:28.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.82,0:35:31.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sir,I need you to go home. All right?\N先生 请你现在回家去 好么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.76,0:35:33.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to go home to your family.\N你现在先回家吧,回到你家人身边去.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.29,0:35:35.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,
What about what I just fucking told you?\N我刚才说的话你他妈没听见么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.06,0:35:37.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you sending someone out to go arrest this guy?\N为什么你们不马上派人去把他抓回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.10,0:35:38.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell detective Loki what you just told me,\N把你刚才告诉我的那些话讲给洛奇警探听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.73,0:35:40.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and he'll definitely look into it.\N他会调查清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.10,0:35:41.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.\N说吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.90,0:35:45.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That asshole you promised me you'd keep in custody,right?\N你跟我保证过你不会放走他的 不是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.67,0:35:47.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't.\N但你并没有那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.27,0:35:49.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And right now when I grabbed him in the parking lot,\N就在刚才 我在停车场抓着他的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.24,0:35:50.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he said right to my fucking face,\N他居然当着我的面说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.98,0:35:52.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,"they didn't cry until I left them."\N『我一走她们就开始哭了』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right to my fucking face.\N当着我的面说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.11,0:35:56.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He... he said that to you in the parking lot just now?\N这话是他刚刚在停车场跟你说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.15,0:35:57.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,yeah. What did I just say?\N对 就是刚才 我不是说了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.78,0:35:59.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,In the parking lot.\N就在停车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.12,0:36:00.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Before you grabbed me off him.\N就在你们把我拉开之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.99,0:36:04.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else hear it besides you?\N当时还有其他人听见他说这话么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.59,0:36:06.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. It was quiet.\N我不知道 他跟我说话时声音很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.36,0:36:09.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He... he said it to me. He wanted me to know.\N他跟我说那些是因为他想让我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.03,0:36:11.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure he said that? What?\N- 你确定他说了那些话? - 什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.10,0:36:13.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's what he said?\N你确定他说了那些话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.80,0:36:16.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ,you think I'm makin' this up?\N老天 你以为这都我是瞎编的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.10,0:36:17.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. Why would I make this up?\N- 不是 - 为什么我要编瞎话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.60,0:36:20.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,hey,hey,whoa,whoa. No,think about it.\N- 嘿 冷静点  - 不 你自己想想.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.27,0:36:22.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I make this up? I'm not saying that to you.\N- 为什么我要骗你 - 我没那么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.11,0:36:24.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just asking you a couple questions.\N我只是问了你几个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.14,0:36:25.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I will talk to him.\N我会跟他谈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.51,0:36:27.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,don't talk to him! Mr. Dover...\N- 别 你别跟这种人『谈』 - 多佛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.05,0:36:29.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,arrest him!\N直接逮捕他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.88,0:36:33.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What did I fuckin' tell you?\N我他妈的怎么跟你说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.65,0:36:36.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I tell you? One more day.\N我他妈怎么跟你说的? 就多一天！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.99,0:36:40.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you didn't say anything to Mr. Dover\N你确定在停车场时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.23,0:36:43.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,in the parking lot today?\N你什么都没跟多佛先生说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.06,0:36:46.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anything he could have misinterpreted or...?\N比如一些让他产生误会的话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.13,0:36:47.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was right there.\N我当时也在那里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.70,0:36:51.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't say anything to each other.\N他们彼此什么话都没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.04,0:36:53.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Man just attacked the boy.\N那男人上来就打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.21,0:36:57.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like "get away from me" or "help" or...\N连『离我远一点』或者『救命』之类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.54,0:36:59.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anything like that?\N类似这样的话都没说过?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.38,0:37:03.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.22,0:37:08.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can I speak to Alex alone for a minute?\N我可以单独跟亚历克斯讲几句话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.66,0:37:13.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right,sweetie.\N没事的 宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.49,0:37:16.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right in the next room.\N我就在隔壁房间等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.37,0:37:30.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You love your aunt,don't you,Alex?\N亚历克斯 你很爱你的姑妈 对吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.55,0:37:37.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N是的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.55,0:37:40.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You know if you know something you're not telling us\N如果你有什么事瞒着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.02,0:37:42.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that she could go to jail for a very long time.\N那可能就会害她坐很长时间的牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.29,0:37:45.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want that for her?\N她为你付出了这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.79,0:37:48.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,After everything she's done for you?\N你不希望她进监狱 对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.63,0:37:51.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.88,0:38:09.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover,this is detective Loki.\N多佛先生 我是洛奇警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.15,0:38:10.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Have you arrested him?\N你有没有逮捕他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.48,0:38:12.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,look,I just came from Alex Jones,\N听着 我刚刚从亚历克斯·琼斯家出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.45,0:38:14.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and he said he didn't say anything to you\N他说他在停车场时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.15,0:38:15.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,in the parking lot.\N什么都没有跟你说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.62,0:38:17.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I pushed him pretty hard,and he didn't budge.\N我不停旁敲侧击 可他还是坚持那套说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.66,0:38:19.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So,look,we can't waste any more time on this guy.\N所以 你听着  我们不能再在他身上浪费时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.89,0:38:21.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right? You're gonna have to trust me.\N好吗？你必须要相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.46,0:38:23.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know if I have anything new,all right,\N如果我这边有任何新的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.10,0:38:24.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,for the...\N我会及时...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.63,0:38:27.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin' A\N有病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.61,0:38:45.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The zipper on her coat was broken,\N我看见她衣服上的拉链坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.15,0:38:46.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and I told her it didn't matter\N可我跟她说没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.79,0:38:48.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,'cause we were just gonna go right down the street.\N因为我们只是到街对面去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.42,0:38:49.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,no.\N不 不.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:49.66,0:38:52.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why hasn't she come home?\N为什么她还没有回家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.59,0:38:53.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three days.\N已经三天了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.93,0:38:57.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you make her come home?\N为什么你还没有把她找回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.60,0:39:00.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.\N我不明白.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.60,0:39:04.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand. It's been too long.\N我真的不明白 已经过去这么长时间了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.87,0:39:09.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please make her come home.\N求你们快把她找回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.01,0:39:11.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please make her...\N求你们..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.45,0:39:14.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How many of these? How many of these?\N这个要吃几片? 几片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.18,0:39:16.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How many of these? I don't know!\N- 一次要吃几片? - 我不知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.22,0:39:17.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's all right.\N没事 别怕 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.65,0:39:20.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just take one.\N就吃一片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.52,0:39:22.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Here.\N拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.49,0:39:24.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.32,0:39:26.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to sleep.\N我只想睡一觉.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.49,0:39:30.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to go to sleep.\N我只想睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.46,0:39:34.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You...\N你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.17,0:39:38.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You made me feel so safe.\N你总能给我安全感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.87,0:39:47.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,
You told us that you could protect us from everything.\N你说过你会保护我们不受任何伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.58,0:39:50.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,God...\N噢 天哪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.05,0:39:56.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go out and help the police.\N我现在要出去协助那些警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:56.42,0:39:58.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep an eye on your mother.\N你照顾好妈妈.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.56,0:40:01.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister needs us to be brave for her.\N为了你妹妹 我们要坚强一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.90,0:40:04.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Be brave for her.Be a grown-up for me,okay?\N你要像个成年人一样 好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:04.73,0:40:06.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?\N你能做到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.17,0:40:08.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?\N能做到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.24,0:40:11.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're scared. Look at me. Come here.\N我知道你很害怕  看着我 过来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.04,0:40:13.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're scared.\N我知道你很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.61,0:40:15.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be okay.\N一切都会好起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.39,0:40:34.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>The former is a reason why we should be very patient.</i>\N<i>前者是我们应耐心等待的理由</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.29,0:40:37.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>The latter why we should be very penitent</i>\N<i>后者则提醒 当我们遭受困苦的时候</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:37.10,0:40:38.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>when we are afflicted.</i>\N<i>理应心生忏悔</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.97,0:40:43.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>He reminds him that trouble and affliction</i>\N<i>困苦与磨难</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.07,0:40:46.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>are what we have all reason to expect in this world.</i>\N<i>是我们生活在这世界所需经受的必须</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.77,0:40:49.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Man is brought into trouble,not as man,</i>\N<i>但困苦并非总是不请自来</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.74,0:40:53.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>but as sinful man,who was in transgression.</i>\N<i>犯下了罪的人 那些僭越的人</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.08,0:40:56.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Man born in sin and therefore born to trouble.</i>\N<i>其人生而有罪 因而必得遭受苦难</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.82,0:42:44.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.69,0:42:47.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,Tucker.\N走啊 塔克.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.06,0:42:50.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Jingle bells,Batman smells</i>\N<i>叮叮当 蝙蝠侠香</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.16,0:42:52.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Robin laid an egg</i>\N<i>罗宾下蛋黄</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.87,0:42:55.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>the Batmobile lost its wheels</i>\N<i>蝙蝠车子轮胎掉</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.87,0:42:58.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>joker got away,hey</i>\N<i>小丑逃跑了 嘿</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.74,0:43:05.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>jingle bells,Batman smells,Robin laid an egg</i>\N<i>叮叮当 蝙蝠侠香 罗宾下蛋黄</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.88,0:43:12.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Jingle bells,Batman smells</i>\N<i>叮叮当 蝙蝠侠香</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.12,0:43:14.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Robin laid an egg</i>\N<i>罗宾下蛋黄</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.79,0:43:17.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>the Batmobile...</i> - Alex.\N<i>蝙蝠车子...</i> - 亚历克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.29,0:43:21.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Lost its wheel...\N<i>轮胎掉...</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.70,0:43:24.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That song.\N那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.90,0:43:27.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear those words?\N你从哪里听到那些歌词的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.80,0:43:32.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?\N啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.09,0:43:55.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring a change of clothes like I told you?\N你有没有按我说的带上一套换洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.00,0:44:00.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.You gonna tell me why?\N带了 能告诉我原因吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.27,0:44:03.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if I just show you.\N你看了就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.10,0:44:07.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what?\N看什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.36,0:44:29.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you used to live here?\N你以前不是住在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.77,0:44:44.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Close the door.Lock it.\N关上门 锁好.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:24.05,0:45:27.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my God.What... what did you do?\N噢 天哪 你都干了些什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.72,0:45:28.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keller,what the hell...?\N凯勒 这里面是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:28.99,0:45:30.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I heard him singing the same song\N我听到他唱歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.72,0:45:32.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,they were singing on Thanksgiving.\N就是女孩们在感恩节那天唱的那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:32.53,0:45:34.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Swear to God,Franklin. The same fucking song.\N我发誓 富兰克林 就是他妈的那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.83,0:45:37.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I told you what he said in the parking lot.\N我已经告诉过你他在停车场对我说过什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.16,0:45:39.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Then we take him to the police...\N那我们把他交给警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.43,0:45:41.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,no,no,no.The police won't do shit.\N不 不 警察狗屁都干不了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:41.20,0:45:43.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just clam up and act crazy like he did last time.\N他还是会继续装疯卖傻不肯说话 就像之前那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.60,0:45:45.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has to make him talk.\N必须得有个人让他开口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.07,0:45:46.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Someone.\N必须得有人这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.74,0:45:54.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shit,man.This... this ain't right.\N可是这么做是不对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:54.01,0:45:55.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,what if you're wrong?\N我是说 万一你错了该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.85,0:45:57.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong. But what if you are?\N- 我没错 - 但是万一...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.92,0:45:59.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What if you only heard what you wanted to hear?\N万一你只是听见了你心里想的东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.42,0:46:01.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What if...\N万一...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.05,0:46:04.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Man,I want my daughter back as much as you do,\N听着 我和你一样想找回自己的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.72,0:46:06.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but it ain't right. Franklin! Franklin!\N- 但这么做是不对的. - 富兰克林 富兰克林!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.56,0:46:11.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We hurt him until he talks,or they're gonna die.\N他不开口 我们就打 不然孩子们都会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.63,0:46:14.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't...\N可是这是不....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.27,0:46:16.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!\N不 别再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.87,0:46:20.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We hurt him until he talks or they're gonna die.\N他不开口 我们就打 不然孩子们都会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.41,0:46:24.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's the choice.\N二选一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:24.41,0:46:27.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's the choice you have to make.\N你必须做出选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:27.15,0:46:29.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I've made my choice.\N我已经做出我的选择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.05,0:46:31.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I heard.\N我知道我听到了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.99,0:46:38.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a person anymore.\N别把他当人看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.56,0:46:44.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,he stopped being a person when he took our daughters.\N从带走我们孩子的那一刻起他就已经不算是人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:51.84,0:46:55.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.\N我需要你的帮助.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:55.28,0:46:58.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance.I know you're scared.\N这是你最后的机会 我知道你很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.34,0:47:00.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I know you wanna go home.\N我知道你想回家.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.48,0:47:03.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't...I don't want to hurt you.\N我不想....不想伤害你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.18,0:47:04.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.\N我不想.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.62,0:47:06.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take the tape off,\N现在我帮你把胶布撕下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.95,0:47:09.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to tell me where they are.\N我要你告诉我孩子们的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.19,0:47:13.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Come on.\N嘿 过来.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.43,0:47:19.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see my glasses?\N你看到我的眼镜了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.27,0:47:20.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.50,0:47:22.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see.\N我看不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.37,0:47:26.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna talk,Alex,I'm gonna have to hurt you.\N如果你不说 亚历克斯 那我就不得不伤害你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:26.04,0:47:28.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where they are.\N告诉我她们在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:28.84,0:47:31.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?\N她们在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.48,0:47:34.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where they are!\N快说 她们在哪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:34.38,0:47:36.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,I'm out here at a house on Fairmont circle,\N对 我在费尔蒙特这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:36.68,0:47:38.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the house the rv was parked in front of.\N就在那辆房车当时停靠的房子前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.62,0:47:40.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been on the market a couple of months.\N几个月前这个房子刚刚转手出售
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.65,0:47:43.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna track the owners down,see if they know anything.\N我准备去找找房主 看看他们是不是知道点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:43.06,0:47:44.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You got any new info on that corpse\N关于之前牧师地下室里的那具尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:44.82,0:47:46.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,we found in the priest's basement?\N你有没有什么新发现？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.53,0:47:49.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No DNA,dental,or fingerprint matches.\N没有DNA 也没找到任何相匹配的牙科记录或指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:49.50,0:47:51.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.\N什么都没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:51.23,0:47:53.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Priest is sticking to the story,too.\N牧师坚称他之前所说的都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.57,0:47:56.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N好吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:26.06,0:48:29.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Same person who took him took those girls.\N我敢肯定 就是带走他的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.90,0:48:32.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.\N带走了那两个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.91,0:48:38.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing out the tape,I guess.\N录像带有点磨损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.01,0:48:40.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I watch it every day after breakfast.\N每天早餐后我都会看这段录像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.55,0:48:42.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only video I have of him.\N这是唯一一卷有他的录像带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:45.12,0:48:48.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It was before your time.\N拍的时候你大概还没出生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:48.02,0:48:51.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,26 years ago,August 19th.\N26年前的8月19日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.93,0:48:54.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I took a nap in the afternoon,\N那天午饭后我小睡了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:54.53,0:48:57.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and when I woke up,Barry was gone.\N等我醒来的时候 巴瑞就不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.46,0:49:00.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No one could ever tell me what happened to him.\N没有人告诉过我究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.53,0:49:03.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He was playing in the front yard,\N他当时就在前院里玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:03.87,0:49:08.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,just a few feet from where they say that rv was parked.\N距离那辆房车停放的地方只有几英尺远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:08.94,0:49:11.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think that means?\N你觉得那意味着什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:15.95,0:49:19.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more interested in what you think that means.\N我更想知道你的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:19.12,0:49:24.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we'll ever know.\N我们可能永远不会知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:24.22,0:49:27.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Barry.\N她们和巴瑞一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:27.59,0:49:29.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No one took them.\N没有人带走她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:29.93,0:49:32.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened.\N就像什么都没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.60,0:49:35.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're just gone.\N就那么凭空消失了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:44.94,0:49:49.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How you doin',father?\N你怎么样 神父?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:49.12,0:49:53.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm...gettin' better.\N我...我感觉好多了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:53.49,0:49:55.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So detective Chemelinski tells me\N季默林斯基警探告诉我说....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:55.36,0:49:57.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that you have some specifics\N你知道一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:57.02,0:50:00.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,about the crime you claim that guy committed.\N关于你说的那个罪犯的细节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.13,0:50:02.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The abductor.\N他是个诱拐犯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:02.16,0:50:05.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He was...\N他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:05.83,0:50:09.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Waging a war against God.\N他要向上帝宣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:12.37,0:50:16.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Great.That's great.\N好吧 好吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.44,0:50:18.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said he had something specific.\N我以为你的意思是说他知道一些细节的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:19.98,0:50:24.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him how he took the kids.\N告诉他那男人是怎么把孩子们带走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:24.35,0:50:27.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He said...\N他说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.29,0:50:32.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he took them in daylight.\N...那些孩子都是他白天带走的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:32.66,0:50:36.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...\N有时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.56,0:50:40.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,More than one child at a time.\N一次还不止一个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:40.07,0:50:42.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He said that?\N他那么说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.04,0:50:44.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N是的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.64,0:50:45.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say he was with anybody?\N他有提到过帮凶的事么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:45.87,0:50:48.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He did it alone?\N还是说他一个人干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.51,0:50:50.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He...\N他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.98,0:50:54.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had a family.\N他说他结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:00.15,0:51:01.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?\N就这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.03,0:51:09.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N好吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.50,0:51:11.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Informative.\N毫无帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.94,0:51:24.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You said they cried when you left them.\N你说过你一走她们就哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:24.54,0:51:25.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.\N看着我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.95,0:51:28.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You said they cried when you left them!\N你说过你走的时候她们在哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:28.85,0:51:32.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You said they cried when you left them!\N你说过你走的时候她们在哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.12,0:51:34.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell me!\N现在你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:34.62,0:51:37.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she? Hmm? Hmm?\N她在哪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.76,0:51:41.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where they are!\N告诉我她们在哪 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.96,0:51:48.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.Just tell me and I'll stop.\N快点说 只要你告诉我我就停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:48.73,0:51:51.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop as soon as you tell me.\N你告诉我 我马上停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:55.81,0:51:57.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just...\N只要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:57.64,0:52:00.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me where they are.\N只要你告诉我她们在哪 .
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.92,0:52:11.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you tell me?\N你为什么不说话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:11.76,0:52:13.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\N啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:15.83,0:52:19.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you just fuckin' tell us?\N为什么你他妈的就是不告诉我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.34,0:52:35.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He knows.\N他知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.31,0:52:38.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He knows.\N他一定知道.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:38.65,0:52:42.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it in his eyes.He fucking knows.\N从他眼睛里看得出来 他肯定他妈的知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:42.42,0:52:45.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you know!\N我知道你知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:45.29,0:52:49.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you fucking telling me?!\N为什么你他妈的就是不告诉我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:49.50,0:52:51.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!\N为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:55.53,0:52:57.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.51,0:53:03.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get him up.Get him up. Get up.\N把他弄起来 弄起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.88,0:53:07.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get up. Get up.Get up!\N起来. 起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:14.29,0:53:16.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna make me use this?\N你打算逼我用这个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.96,0:53:18.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna tell us?\N你说不说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.79,0:53:22.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't,I'm gonna use this.\N如果你不说我就要用这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.86,0:53:24.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.23,0:53:31.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing this to yourself.\N这是你自找的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:31.14,0:53:35.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us.Tell me.\N快说 告诉我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:35.51,0:53:37.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!\N告诉我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:39.41,0:53:41.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!\N告诉我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.68,0:53:44.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Tell me!\N告诉我!告诉我!告诉我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.92,0:53:46.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my daughter?!\N我女儿在哪里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.99,0:53:50.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where's... My...Daughter?!\N我女儿 ！在！哪里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:12.34,0:54:14.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Four days have passed</i>\N<i>从安娜·多佛和乔伊·伯奇的父母</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.38,0:54:15.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>since Anna Dover and Joy Birch</i>\N<i>最后一次看见她们</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.88,0:54:17.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>were last seen by their families.</i>\N<i>到现在已经过去四天了</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:17.62,0:54:19.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>The two girls,aged 6 and 7,</i>\N<i>这两个小女孩 分别只有6岁和7岁</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:19.39,0:54:21.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>are believed to have been playing on this street</i>\N<i>警方认为女孩们失踪前</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:21.42,0:54:23.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>when they disappeared without a trace.</i>\N<i>正在街上玩耍</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:23.39,0:54:25.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>As you can see,despite the cold,</i>\N<i>正如你所看到的 尽管今晚天气很冷</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:25.26,0:54:28.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>a lot of people have turned out tonight to show their support.\N<i>但依然有许许多多的人来到街上 为两位女孩祈祷</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.23,0:54:29.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Police are asking that anyone</i>\N<i>警方表示 如果任何人</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:29.96,0:54:32.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>with any information on the girls' whereabouts...</i>\N<i>知道有关两位女孩下落的信息....</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.41,0:54:46.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?\N你去哪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:46.61,0:54:50.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was searching for her in the woods.\N我一直在树林里找她.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:08.40,0:55:10.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. I'm okay.\N我没事 我没事.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:10.64,0:55:12.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Franklin.\N富兰克林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:12.84,0:55:15.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Franklin,what is it?\N富兰克林 你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.51,0:55:18.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just need a minute.\N我很快就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.98,0:58:41.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck?\N搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:41.28,0:58:43.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get offa me!\N嘿 放开我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:45.68,0:58:48.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!\N嘿 嘿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.69,0:59:29.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>And this is who police are saying</i>\N<i>这位就是警方公示的</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.70,0:59:31.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>is a person of interest</i>\N<i>与两名女孩的失踪案...</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.40,0:59:33.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>in the investigation of the two missing girls.</i>\N<i>有关的嫌疑人</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.20,0:59:35.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Now,this unidentified man,</i>\N<i>该不明身份男子</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.03,0:59:37.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>who was last seen at last night's candlelight vigil,</i>\N<i>最后一次出现是在昨晚的烛光守夜现场</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.10,0:59:39.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>fled on foot when the investigating detective</i>\N<i>当负责该案件的警探试图盘查他时</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:39.74,0:59:41.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>attempted to question him.</i>\N<i>该男子当即从现场逃脱</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:41.57,0:59:44.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Police caution the public not to approach this man,</i>\N<i>警方警告公众 请勿接近这名男子</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.11,0:59:45.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>but to call police immediately if they do see him.</i>\N<i>如果有人发现该男子 请立即报警</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:47.71,0:59:49.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Thanks,John,for that update.</i>\N<i>谢谢约翰为我们带来的最新消息</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.55,0:59:51.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>And now for the weather.</i>\N<i>现在我们来看看天气状况</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:51.75,0:59:54.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>We should expect heavy rain into the weekend and...</i>\N<i>本周末我们将迎来一场暴雨...</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:04.86,1:00:06.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,Keller,I mean,just think about it.\N听着 凯勒 你好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:06.63,1:00:08.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the police be lookin' for this man\N如果警察认为不是这个男人干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.47,1:00:10.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,if they didn't think that he did it in the first place?\N为什么他们要寻找他.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:10.74,1:00:12.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They did it together.They know each other.\N他们肯定是同伙 他们认识彼此.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.54,1:00:14.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Listen,I fuckin' told you,all right?\N听着 我早他妈的告诉过你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.91,1:00:17.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jones looked me in the eye and he said,\N琼斯看着我的眼睛说……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.31,1:00:18.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,"they only cried when I left them."\N『我一走她们就开始哭了』
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.94,1:00:21.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He left 'em with someone,and he knows where this guy is.\N他把她们留在某个人那里 而且他知道那个人在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.09,1:00:29.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Holly Jones' dog got hit on southward street.\N亚历克斯·琼斯的狗在南大街被车撞了	
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:29.99,1:00:31.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Alex Jones took the dog for a walk\N很显然亚历克斯·琼斯当时正在遛狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.79,1:00:33.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the night before last...they never came home.\N前天晚上 那之后他一直没有回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.63,1:00:35.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And his aunt didn't want to tell us about the dog\N他姑妈没老实把那只狗的事告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:35.59,1:00:37.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when we called her about it this morning.\N今天早晨我们打电话给她的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.26,1:00:38.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she thought\N她解释说她觉得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:38.60,1:00:40.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,it would get him into trouble or some shit.\N那会让他惹上麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:40.17,1:00:42.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said you would keep him under surveillance.\N我以为你会安排人监视他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:42.27,1:00:44.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,and I thought you said the guy was innocent.\N我以为你说那个男人是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.27,1:00:46.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought the guy from last night you said was our guy.\N而且我还以为昨晚那个人才是我们要找的人.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:46.61,1:00:47.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I don't have money in the budget\N听着 我没那么多经费
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:47.94,1:00:49.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,for watching innocent people.\N去监视一个无辜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.48,1:00:51.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You said to me that you'd put him under surveillance.\N但你跟我说你会安排人监视他.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.11,1:00:53.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say? You gonna keep your word?\N- 那你想让我说什么? - 你说话就不能算点数吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:53.25,1:00:54.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just given me a call,because I would have\N哪怕你就给我打个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.81,1:00:56.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,been there all night. I would have stayed up all night.\N那我会待在那里看着他 哪怕熬通宵都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:56.08,1:00:57.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I would know where he was now.\N起码我现在就可以知道他去了哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:57.35,1:00:59.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know where everybody is.\N我需要知道每个人待在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.08,1:01:01.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,point made. All right? Point made.\N行了 我知道了 行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:01.19,1:01:03.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If you can be clear with me,then I'll be clear with you.\N你把事整干脆了 我也能和你干脆点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.92,1:01:05.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know where everybody is.\N我需要知道每个人待在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.69,1:01:08.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna do something different,please tell me.\N下次如果你要变更计划 请提前告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:08.33,1:01:11.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Tell me about your RV.</i>\N<i>告诉我有关房车的事</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:11.26,1:01:12.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>What do you do in your RV?</i>\N<i>你在房车里做什么</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.60,1:01:15.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>It's where I go...</i>\N<i>我想一个人呆着的时候</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:15.87,1:01:17.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>To be alone.</i>\N<i>就会去那里</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:21.97,1:01:27.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>What music do you listen to in your RV when you're alone?</i>\N<i>你一个人在车里听些什么</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.31,1:01:30.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Radio,tape...</i>\N<i>广播 还有磁带</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:33.65,1:01:37.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>The RV was parked over on Fairmont circle?</i>\N<i>房车停在费尔蒙特一带？</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:37.99,1:01:39.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>No.</i>\N<i>没有</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.96,1:01:41.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Is my aunt coming?</i>\N<i>我姑妈来了吗?</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:47.83,1:01:50.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Have you seen these girls?</i>\N<i>你见过这两个女孩吗?</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:50.20,1:01:51.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>No.</i>\N<i>没有</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:51.74,1:01:55.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Take a look at 'em.You seen these girls?</i>\N<i>再看看照片 你有没有见过她们？</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.21,1:01:58.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>No.</i>\N<i>没有.</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:58.81,1:02:01.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>Did you participate in any way</i>\N<i>你有没有以任何形式参与...</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:01.31,1:02:03.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>in the abduction of those girls?</i>\N<i>绑架这两个女孩?</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:03.88,1:02:05.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,<i>No.</i>\N<i>没有</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.25,1:02:09.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Loki! You got a call.\N洛奇 你的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.42,1:02:13.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\N来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.86,1:02:17.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I called as soon as I saw the sketch on TV.\N我一在电视上看到嫌犯画像就打来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:17.56,1:02:19.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He comes in here every week almost\N他几乎每周都会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.36,1:02:20.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and buys kids' clothes,\N买小孩子的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.87,1:02:23.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but he's always buying stuff in different sizes.\N但是他每次买的都是不同尺寸的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.44,1:02:26.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Caught him messing around with the mannequins once.\N有次他在人体模特附近搞破坏被抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:26.17,1:02:27.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What did he pay with?\N他用什么付款?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.67,1:02:30.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Cash.\N现金.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.18,1:02:32.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,you give me a call if you hear anything.\N好 如果你有什么消息 及时打电话给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.88,1:02:34.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.45,1:02:40.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five days.\N已经第五天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.35,1:02:44.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe five days since they had a drink of water.\N也许她们已经五天没喝水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.56,1:02:48.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This could be the last night that matters.\N也许过了今晚就来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.90,1:02:55.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I'll call you after Nancy goes to sleep,all right?\N听着 南茜睡着后我再打给你 好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:55.63,1:02:57.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.\N我保证.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.80,1:03:32.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been all this time?\N这段时间你都在哪 ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:04.44,1:04:06.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you thinking?\N你到底怎么想的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:15.68,1:04:18.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You tell anyone?\N你没有告诉其他人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:18.48,1:04:20.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?\N有没有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.96,1:04:26.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see him.\N我想要见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.39,1:05:33.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.\N请帮帮我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:37.23,1:05:40.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help me find my little girl?\N可以帮我找我的小女儿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:43.40,1:05:45.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Got a picture.\N我带了一张照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:45.54,1:05:48.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,See?\N看到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:48.37,1:05:52.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This my baby.\N这是我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:52.08,1:05:54.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You see her?\N看见了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:54.45,1:05:58.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is joy.\N她的名字叫乔伊.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.45,1:06:05.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And,um...\N还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.59,1:06:07.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is...\N这个是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:07.43,1:06:09.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,A stuffed animal we got her when she was 2\N这是她两岁的时候我们买给她的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.93,1:06:12.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,because she's afraid to sleep by herself.\N因为那时她不敢一个人睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:12.00,1:06:14.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Tell me where my little girl is.\N求求你...告诉我 我女儿在哪里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.83,1:06:19.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me where my little girl...\N求求你告诉我 我女儿在哪....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.84,1:06:25.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're gonna tell me.\N我知道你会告诉我的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:25.81,1:06:28.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're gonna tell me.\N我知道你会告诉我的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:28.41,1:06:30.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\N我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:48.60,1:06:51.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.\N帮帮我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:51.04,1:06:54.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.\N帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:54.34,1:06:56.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Franklin,did you close the door to the...\N富兰克林,你有没有把门关....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.81,1:06:59.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy!\N南茜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:01.71,1:07:04.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck you doin'?\N你他妈的在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:06.52,1:07:08.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!Damn!\N该死的！见鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:08.35,1:07:11.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go!\N把它放下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:11.32,1:07:13.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go!\N把它放下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.03,1:07:20.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You untied him? Huh?\N你把他的绳子解开了？啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:32.31,1:07:33.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.\N差点就让你跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.79,1:08:17.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What happened?\N怎么了？发生什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:17.46,1:08:20.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get Franklin.I need to show you something.\N叫上富兰克林 我要给你们看点东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:23.53,1:08:25.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything new?\N他有没有说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:25.43,1:08:27.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He will soon.You'll see.\N很快就会说的 等着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:38.48,1:08:42.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No light gets in.\N没有光线.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:42.45,1:08:44.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,There's barely enough room to sit down inside.\N里面的位置也不够他坐下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.62,1:08:45.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shower still works,\N莲蓬头还能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:45.88,1:08:47.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but we control it from out here.\N但控制阀门在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:47.59,1:08:49.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I rigged the water heater\N我把加热器改装过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:49.92,1:08:53.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,so it either comes out scalding or freezing.\N出来的水不是滚烫就是冰冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:55.73,1:08:58.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And,uh,you talk to him through this.\N你可以从这里和他说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.73,1:09:00.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's to remind us...\N这是为了提醒我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.60,1:09:04.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,In case we start feeling sorry for him.\N以防我们动恻隐之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:04.14,1:09:08.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My God.\N我的天.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:08.27,1:09:10.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hurt him any more without killing him,\N我们不能杀他 所以这是最能折磨他的办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:10.68,1:09:11.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,so this is the only way.\N这也是唯一的方法.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:11.94,1:09:14.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind,Keller?\N你疯了吗？凯勒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.91,1:09:17.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a better idea,Franklin?\N难道你有更好的主意 富兰克林?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.68,1:09:21.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?\N有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:21.15,1:09:23.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.Let him out,if you want.\N去吧 放他出来 如果你想的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:23.79,1:09:25.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna stop you.\N我不拦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:25.46,1:09:28.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you really want,you go ahead.\N如果你真想那么做 就动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:28.66,1:09:31.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You think someone's lookin' out for our girls\N你现在在这里可怜他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:31.20,1:09:33.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the way you're lookin' out for him?\N谁来可怜我们的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:33.30,1:09:37.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I hope.\N希望有这么个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:37.17,1:09:42.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five days now,man.We're runnin' out of time.\N已经五天了 我们快没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.04,1:09:44.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know it's him.\N你还不能确定就是他干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:44.18,1:09:45.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,I do. No,you don't.\N- 我能确定 - 不 你不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.71,1:09:49.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I do. I know you. You don't.\N- 我很确定. - 我知道你不确定.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:49.78,1:09:54.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,I want my baby back...\N听着 我现在和你心情一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.35,1:09:57.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,As much as you miss Anna.\N我也想让我的安娜快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:57.29,1:10:00.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And despite what you think about me,\N我不在乎你是怎么看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.16,1:10:03.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I would die for my daughter.\N可是我可以为了我的女儿去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:03.20,1:10:06.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But this ain't right.\N但我们这么做是不对的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:06.16,1:10:08.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This has to stop.\N我们不能再这样下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:08.90,1:10:13.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,then,you better get to work.\N那你就动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:15.74,1:10:19.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You can start with that wall there.\N从那面墙开始拆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:35.69,1:10:38.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Franklin.\N富兰克林.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.83,1:10:42.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.\N别
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:48.11,1:10:49.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Franklin...\N富兰克林...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.61,1:10:51.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Think of joy.\N想想乔伊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:31.45,1:11:34.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get out of this place,Ralph.\N我得走了 拉尔夫.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:34.82,1:11:39.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this house just makes me want to throw up.\N这房子里的一切都让我想吐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.09,1:11:43.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's building?\N你是说你爸爸的房子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.33,1:11:47.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I'm staying in that crackhouse.\N我没办法待在那个破房子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.00,1:11:50.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's disgusting.\N太恶心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.60,1:11:53.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,okay.\N好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.69,1:12:20.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna help Keller,but we won't stop him,either.\N我们不会帮凯勒 但我们也不能阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.77,1:12:22.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let him do what he needs to.\N就让他做他想做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:28.54,1:12:31.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know about it anymore.\N我们不要再管那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.47,1:12:57.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza?\N伊莱扎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:59.24,1:13:01.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza?\N伊莱扎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:06.58,1:13:09.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.Eliza?\N伊莱扎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:10.71,1:13:13.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza,open the door!\N伊莱扎 开开门.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:13.89,1:13:15.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza?\N伊莱扎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:15.25,1:13:16.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in there?\N她在里面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:16.86,1:13:18.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Honey?\N亲爱的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.99,1:13:20.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!Get out of the way!\N让开! 让开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.89,1:13:22.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,fuck you both!\N你们俩够了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.43,1:13:24.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you plan on leaving me here alone,\N下次你们如果打算留我一人在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.60,1:13:27.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you could try at least telling me where you're going!\N请至少跟我说清楚你们要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:30.76,1:14:32.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ralph?\N拉尔夫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.40,1:14:39.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:39.40,1:14:41.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:44.11,1:14:47.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:50.51,1:14:52.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:01.03,1:15:04.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.46,1:15:09.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?\N妈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:12.47,1:15:13.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?\N妈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.87,1:15:15.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna.Anna was here.\N安娜. 安娜刚刚在这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:15.14,1:15:16.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mom,it's freezing in here.\N妈 这里怎么这么冷.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:16.71,1:15:19.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Hey,mom,mom,mom,please sit down.\N妈! 嘿 妈 妈 你先坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:19.28,1:15:21.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Calm down.I'm gonna close the window.\N别说了 冷静点 我去把窗户关上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:23.81,1:15:26.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And she wasn't here.\N她不在这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:26.85,1:15:30.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And then I heard a sound from my room,\N然后我听到我房间里有动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.49,1:15:33.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and I... I came in and the window was open.\N然后...我发现窗户是开着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:33.66,1:15:37.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And... and it wasn't open before.\N并且...窗户之前一直是关着的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:37.46,1:15:42.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And then... and then Ralph,he... he came in...\N然后 拉尔夫进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:42.20,1:15:45.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And he looked and... and,um...\N他看着我...然后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:45.74,1:15:49.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And then...\N然后..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:49.04,1:15:52.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't know.\N然后...我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:52.51,1:15:55.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna write this down?\N你要不要把这些写下来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:05.92,1:16:09.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The basement.\N地下室.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.93,1:16:11.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't check the basement. We need to check the basement.\N没有检查地下室 我们得去检查一下地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:11.93,1:16:14.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll show you. I'll show you.\N我带你去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:25.08,1:16:28.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The kids know they're not allowed down here.\N我们不允许孩子们下来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:32.92,1:16:35.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're not supposed to come down here,\N他们不应该下来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:35.85,1:16:37.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but I-I don't know.\N但是 谁知道呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:54.10,1:16:58.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My husband likes to be prepared for emergencies.\N我丈夫喜欢为紧急状况做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.65,1:17:06.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your husband,Mrs. Dover?\N你丈夫去哪了 多佛太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:06.42,1:17:08.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna ask you.\N我也正想问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:08.05,1:17:11.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's been out searching with the police for Anna.\N他一直在外边忙着和警察一起找安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:11.76,1:17:14.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Which you should be doing right now.\N你现在不也该去找的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:14.83,1:17:17.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Does he always stay out this late?\N他总是在外边待到这么晚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:17.66,1:17:20.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,he stays out this late\N对 他总是在很晚才回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:20.57,1:17:22.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when he's looking for my daughter,\N每次他说要出去找我们女儿的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.10,1:17:23.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,since my daughter has been gone... yes!\N从我们的女儿不见开始...是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:23.50,1:17:24.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.\N该死.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:51.32,1:18:52.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,go aro...\N嘿 你绕道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:52.76,1:18:54.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,go around.\N从边上绕过去.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.43,1:19:07.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.\N该死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:50.71,1:19:55.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,Mr. Dover.\N快点吧 多佛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:00.16,1:20:03.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.\N该死.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:16.11,1:20:19.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you following me?\N你为什么跟踪我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:19.64,1:20:21.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the car.\N上车说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:34.36,1:20:36.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you following me?\N你为什么要跟踪我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:39.86,1:20:42.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go just now?\N你刚才去哪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:42.67,1:20:44.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I parked at a liquor store.\N我去那边的商店里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:44.80,1:20:46.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bottle of liquor.\N买了瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.84,1:20:50.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're the shit-hot detective.Work it out.\N你不是神探么 这都看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:50.31,1:20:52.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I actually meant before that.\N我是说你进商店前本来准备去哪 ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.68,1:20:57.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You were walking in the opposite direction\N你往商店的反方向走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:57.18,1:20:59.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,across the parking lot.\N穿过停车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:59.12,1:21:01.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Towards campello street.\N往坎佩罗大街方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:09.13,1:21:11.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,well... I haven't had a drink\N这个... 我已经有大概9年半
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:11.80,1:21:13.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,in nine-and-a-half years.\N没喝过酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:13.63,1:21:16.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I figured if I walked around the parking lot for a while,\N我以为在商店开门的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:16.30,1:21:18.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,by the time they opened,I'd stop wanting it that bad.\N在停车场周围走走 就不会那么犯瘾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:18.84,1:21:21.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And then... then I saw you.\N然后 我就看到了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.41,1:21:24.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sorta helped me make up my mind.\N我就忍不住去买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.81,1:21:33.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bag of lye in your basement that's half-empty.\N你地下室里的碱液 有一袋用了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:36.02,1:21:41.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife thinks you've been helpin' us...\N你妻子以为你一直在帮我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:41.69,1:21:45.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But we both know that's not true.\N但我们都知道那不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.26,1:21:47.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I used the lye to bury our dog last year.\N去年我埋葬我们家的狗时用掉了一部分碱液
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:47.67,1:21:49.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And "helping the cops" sounds better\N而且,我之所以说『我在帮警察』是因为这话听起来要比...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:49.70,1:21:52.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,than "I've been driving aimlessly in my truck\N『我开着车在四处游荡』要好得多是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:52.20,1:21:54.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,'cause I don't know what the fuck else to do."\N因为我不知道我他妈的还能做点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.74,1:21:56.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you were doing last Saturday night?\N上周六晚上你也在四处闲晃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:56.94,1:22:00.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.Am I a suspect?\N可能吧 我现在是嫌疑犯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:00.01,1:22:01.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,I'm only asking\N不 我就随便问问
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:01.75,1:22:04.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only asking 'cause you assaulted a man who's now missing.\N你袭击过的那个男人失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:04.28,1:22:09.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about that.What happened to him?\N我听说了 他怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:09.12,1:22:11.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you had him under surveillance.\N我以为你们在监视他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:11.19,1:22:12.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna assume you're asking me because you have no idea.\N我以为你这么问是因为你也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:12.92,1:22:15.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,I didn't think it was something I could get away with.\N我不认为你会觉得我跟这事没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.06,1:22:17.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.\N不是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:17.06,1:22:18.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,well,it couldn't be that he skipped town\N他该不是畏罪潜逃了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:18.90,1:22:21.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,'cause the asshole is guilty. Couldn't be that,right?\N不可能是那样 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:21.10,1:22:23.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause that would mean it would be your fault,right?\N因为如果是那样 那就是你的失职 不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:23.60,1:22:25.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover?\N多佛先生.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:28.27,1:22:30.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover? What?\N- 多佛先生. - 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:30.31,1:22:33.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take care of yourself and your wife.\N你得照顾好自己和妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.88,1:22:37.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best thing you can do right now.\N这是目前你能做的最有用的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:37.08,1:22:41.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That little girl is gonna need you when she comes home.\N等你女儿回来时 她也需要你的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:44.49,1:22:46.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Kids gone for more than a week\N我女儿已经失踪一周多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:46.46,1:22:49.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,have half as good a chance of being found,\N找到她的机会已经减半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.06,1:22:51.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and after a month,almost none are.\N如果超过一个月,那机会就等于零了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:51.26,1:22:52.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Not alive. All right?\N即使找到她  她可能也已经死了 对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.66,1:22:55.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So forgive me for doing everything I can...\N所以 请原谅我不得不竭尽所能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.17,1:22:57.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?It hasn't been a fucking week.\N现在连一周都还没到呢 你明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:57.44,1:22:59.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's day fucking six!\N你说得对 现在已经是他妈的第六天了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:59.00,1:23:00.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Day six!\N第六天!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:00.60,1:23:03.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And every day she's wondering why\N每一天 她肯定都在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:03.74,1:23:06.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not there to fucking rescue her!\N为什么我他妈的还没去救她.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.08,1:23:07.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Do you understand that?!\N你明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:07.28,1:23:10.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Not you! Not you! But me!\N着急的是我 是我 不是你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.28,1:23:12.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Every day!\N每天都是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:13.82,1:23:17.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So forgive me for not going home to have a good night's rest!\N原谅我现在还不能回家好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:17.76,1:23:19.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now,why don't you look\N现在,为什么你他妈的不去找我的女儿·
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.69,1:23:23.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,for my fucking daughter rather than fighting...\N而要在这里和我.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:23.63,1:23:25.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,hey,hey,hey,hey,hey,hey.\N嘿 嘿 嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:25.13,1:23:27.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me.\N别跟着我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:27.10,1:23:29.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover. Mr. Dover.\N多佛先生 多佛先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:37.14,1:23:38.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think I'm gonna let you get behind the wheel\N你喝了这么多酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:38.71,1:23:40.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,after you've been drinkin',do you?\N你觉得我现在还能让你继续开车吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:40.34,1:23:42.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna walk.\NYou look for my daughter.\N我走回去 你去找我的女儿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:27.36,1:24:28.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.\N爸爸.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:28.89,1:24:31.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.\N爸爸.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:31.33,1:24:33.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,daddy,we found it.\N爸爸你看 我们找到了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:36.10,1:24:40.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna... Where was it?\N安娜 在哪找到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.27,1:26:26.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Alex.\N我不是亚历克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:36.49,1:26:39.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Alex.\N我不是亚历克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:39.46,1:26:43.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What... what are you saying? What? What?\N什么,你说什么? 什么?什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:43.13,1:26:47.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... Not... Alex.\N我...不是...亚历克斯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.33,1:26:48.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. You're not Alex? What?\N等一下 你不是亚历克斯? 什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:48.63,1:26:51.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Alex.\N我不是亚历克斯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.50,1:26:54.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second. I don't understand.\N等一下,我不明白.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:54.97,1:26:56.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just... just talk to me.\N告诉我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:56.64,1:27:00.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I waited,and he never came.\N我一直在等 可他一直没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:00.31,1:27:01.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. No more riddles.\N得了 别再跟我玩谜语了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:01.71,1:27:04.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just fuckin' tell me.\N快他妈的告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:06.52,1:27:09.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go home to your aunt\N我就让你回家 回去你姑妈那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.25,1:27:11.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,if you tell me where they are.\N如果你告诉我她们在哪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:11.89,1:27:16.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to play.\N我只是想找他玩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.89,1:27:19.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me do this again.\N别再逼我做这种事了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:19.20,1:27:21.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And he never came. Don't make me do it.\N- 可是他没有来 - 别逼我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:21.53,1:27:25.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He never came.\N他没有来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:25.07,1:27:27.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to...\N我只是想....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:27.07,1:27:29.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,why are you making me do this?\N为什么你一定要逼我这么做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:46.56,1:27:49.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help me,God.\N主 请帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:52.93,1:27:55.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on your almighty power\N以你全知全能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.40,1:27:58.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and infinite mercies and promises,\N无尽的仁慈以庇佑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:58.44,1:28:02.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to obtain pardon for my sins.\N宽恕我的罪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:34.14,1:28:36.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck me.\N坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:41.24,1:28:44.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No... no noise.You shut up.\N别出声 你最好乖乖闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.08,1:28:47.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You make any noise,I'm gonna turn on that tap.\N你弄出任何动静 我就会打开水龙头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:36.17,1:29:37.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,rise and shine.\N嘿 太阳晒屁股了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:43.57,1:29:45.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna find two girls here,am I?\N两个小女孩总不会藏在这吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:45.51,1:29:47.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you.\N去你妈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:53.08,1:29:55.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What about Alex Jones?\N亚历克斯·琼斯怎么样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.02,1:29:57.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?\N他什么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:57.89,1:29:59.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to drink.\N我过来这喝酒而已.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:59.72,1:30:03.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to drink in front of my wife.\N我不想在我妻子面前喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:03.33,1:30:07.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look... My father left me this building,all right?\N听着 这是我父亲留给我的房子 明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:09.50,1:30:13.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You mind giving me a tour?\N你介意带我参观一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:23.25,1:30:25.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me about this place?\N为什么你没有跟我提过这个地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.72,1:30:28.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it mattered.\N这和案子没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.25,1:30:31.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Everything matters.\N任何事都有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.22,1:30:36.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's all pretty much like this.\N房子比较破旧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.43,1:30:38.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna renovate soon.\N我正准备重修装修呢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.06,1:30:39.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N嗯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:39.46,1:30:41.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Not as organized as your basement,huh?\N没你的地下室整齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:45.23,1:30:48.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with all the survivor gear in there?\N这些生存装备是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.61,1:30:51.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Pray for the best,prepare for the worst.\N祈求最好的结果 做好最坏的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.78,1:30:54.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we agree there,yeah?\N我也常这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:55.61,1:30:57.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,hurry up.\N快点 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:31.35,1:31:34.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.\N该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:36.82,1:31:38.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\N喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.46,1:31:43.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The guy that you were looking for was just here.\N你要找的那个人刚刚来过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:43.99,1:31:45.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He saw me watching him and ran.\N他发现我在看他 然后他就跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:45.76,1:31:47.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You get a plate?\N记下他的车牌号了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:51.67,1:31:54.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:56.14,1:31:59.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.81,1:32:03.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:03.21,1:32:05.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go home,Mr. Dover.\N回家去吧 多佛先生.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.41,1:32:35.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.\N嗨.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:35.68,1:32:37.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'.\N早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:47.06,1:32:50.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you run away from me the other night,man?\N那晚你为什么要逃跑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:50.43,1:32:54.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you before.\N我从来没有见过你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:54.77,1:32:58.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you have the right house?\N你没敲错门吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:58.04,1:33:01.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You doin' some shopping at the value mall lately?\N你最近有去那家商场买东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:01.94,1:33:03.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:03.87,1:33:06.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Is it a crime to shop there?\N为什么这么问？去那里买东西有罪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:06.28,1:33:09.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to buy suits from Brooks Brothers.\N我又买不起布克兄弟那种档次的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:14.62,1:33:16.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,I know.\N我知道.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:16.62,1:33:19.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You bought children's clothes.\N你买的是小孩的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:19.36,1:33:22.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?\N有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:22.13,1:33:25.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been in a hurry.\N我不记得 可能当时太仓促了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:29.93,1:33:32.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do... do you have children?\N你有孩子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:32.37,1:33:34.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没有.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:36.21,1:33:39.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...Have...\N我什么....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:39.64,1:33:41.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Have anything...\N.....什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:44.11,1:33:46.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Christ!\N老实点 该死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:53.46,1:33:56.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your fucking hand.\N把手给我伸过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:00.40,1:34:02.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:02.50,1:34:06.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,If you move,I'll put a bullet through your fuckin' head.\N如果你敢跑 我就照你脑门来一枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:24.99,1:34:26.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,This is 13-40.\N这里是警员13-40.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.29,1:34:28.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need additional unit for search.\N我需要一支小队支援搜查...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:28.03,1:34:29.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,437 Carrol street.\N请派警员前往凯勒街437号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:29.46,1:34:31.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Possible kidnapping victims on the premises.\N受害者可能就在屋内
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:20.84,1:35:23.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:23.88,1:35:26.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna? Joy?\N安娜? 乔伊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:26.65,1:35:29.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.\N操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:37.76,1:35:40.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.\N操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:22.04,1:36:23.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Fuck.\N我操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:30.28,1:36:31.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.\N噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:04.61,1:37:08.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Fuck.\N我操！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:09.59,1:37:11.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.\N噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:22.30,1:37:24.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So we've taken photographs of some of the clothing\N我们已经给那些在嫌疑犯的房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.67,1:37:26.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,we found in the suspect's house.\N找到的衣服拍了照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:08.24,1:38:10.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover.\N多佛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:14.98,1:38:17.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dover,is your wife here?\N多佛先生,你妻子在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:24.19,1:38:27.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming.\N她没来.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:27.73,1:38:29.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,if you can't make a positive I.D.\N好吧,如果你无法准确地辨认
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:29.67,1:38:31.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,On any of these photographs\N这些照片里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:31.37,1:38:33.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna need her to come in and take a look at them.\N那你的妻子就需要亲自来确认一趟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:40.21,1:38:42.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.\N请坐.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:52.35,1:38:56.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So he confessed? He said he killed them?\N他是不是已经认罪了？他把她们杀了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:56.26,1:38:58.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We were hoping he was lying,but...\N我们希望他是在撒谎 但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:58.53,1:39:02.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even found any bodies,Mr. Dover,but...\N我们还没有找到任何尸体 不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:06.24,1:39:08.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the birches positively identified\N...伯奇先生和太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:08.81,1:39:11.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,two pieces of clothing.\N已经指认了两件他们女儿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:11.24,1:39:12.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna need you...\N如果你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:12.81,1:39:16.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna need you to tell me if you recognize anything.\N如果你能认出什么 请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:37.63,1:39:39.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:47.61,1:39:51.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.\N我不确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:51.35,1:39:52.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\N我不知道.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:58.65,1:40:00.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:07.20,1:40:10.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:27.48,1:40:31.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That... That's her...\N那...那是她的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:36.49,1:40:38.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's her sock.\N那是她的袜子.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:53.54,1:40:55.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You...\N你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:58.68,1:41:01.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You wasted time.\N你把时间浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:06.49,1:41:10.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You wasted time following me.\N你浪费时间去跟踪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:18.73,1:41:20.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You let this happen.\N是你害死了她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:59.98,1:42:02.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to them.\N不要跟他们讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:09.15,1:42:12.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza told me they're dead.\N伊莱扎和我说她们已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:13.76,1:42:15.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?\N真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:15.76,1:42:17.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:17.39,1:42:20.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She said they found their bloody clothes\N她说警察找到了沾着她们血的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.23,1:42:21.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,don't you tell your mother that.\N别告诉你妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:21.56,1:42:22.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare tell your mother that.\N不能告诉你妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:22.60,1:42:23.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You understand me?\N听明白了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:23.83,1:42:25.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now,I need you to listen to me.\N现在你听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:25.64,1:42:27.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to stay around the house for a couple of days,\N这几天你留在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:27.67,1:42:29.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and you make sure she does not watch the news,\N你要保证不能让她看到新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:29.67,1:42:31.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and when the paper comes,\N如果有报纸送来,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:31.27,1:42:32.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you just throw itthe fuck away... listen to me!\N你就把它们丢掉.听着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:32.81,1:42:35.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We do not give up on your sister!\N我们还不能放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:35.11,1:42:36.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We do not!\N我们不能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:36.58,1:42:38.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna find her.I'm gonna bring her home.\N我会找到她的 我会带她回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:38.98,1:42:40.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We do not give up.\N不能放弃.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:40.75,1:42:42.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna bring her home? She's dead.\N你要带她回家？ 她已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:42.42,1:42:43.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything.\N你现在什么都做不了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:43.92,1:42:45.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You've been leavin' me and mom here while you...\N你把我和妈妈扔在这里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:45.32,1:42:47.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you've been goin' out and getting fuckin' drunk!\N自己跑到外边去喝个烂醉..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:47.26,1:42:48.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can't smell it on you?!\N你以为我闻不到你身上的酒味吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:48.66,1:42:50.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\N闭嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:11.78,1:43:16.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How long has this Bob Taylor been workin' on this map?\N这个鲍勃·泰勒折腾这张地图多久了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:16.32,1:43:17.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Three-and-a-half hours.\N三个半小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:17.85,1:43:20.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And you think this is gonna lead you to the bodies?\N你觉得这能让你找到那些尸体?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:20.49,1:43:22.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I sure as shit don't.\N我知道那是不可能的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:22.23,1:43:24.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favor,captain.Go fuck yourself.\N帮我个忙 巡查长 滚一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:24.63,1:43:27.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't getting anywhere questioning him.\N问了半天什么都没问出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:31.70,1:43:34.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That looks more like a maze than a map.\N与其说那画像地图 不如说是迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:34.20,1:43:35.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a thing for mazes.\N他热衷迷宫一类的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:39.14,1:43:42.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm goin' home.Call me if somethin' happens.\N我先回家了  如果有什么进展 打电话给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:25.42,1:44:28.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that card,Johnny.The key card.\N把门禁卡递给我 约翰尼 卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:38.53,1:44:40.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,it's done now.\N好了 你已经画完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:42.07,1:44:45.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you're drawing.\N告诉我你画的是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:45.38,1:44:47.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were drawing a map.\N你说你要画一张地图,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:47.28,1:44:49.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a fucking puzzle.\N可是这玩意看起来明明是一个迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:49.28,1:44:51.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me what you're drawing.\N告诉你我画的是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.75,1:44:57.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you're drawing.\N告诉你我画的是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:59.96,1:45:01.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!\N我不能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:01.26,1:45:04.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,you can!Yes,you can!Oh,shit!\N你当然可以说 你当然能 该死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:04.39,1:45:05.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!\N该死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:05.76,1:45:08.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,you can!Yes,you can!\N你必须说!必须说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:08.00,1:45:11.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Take him! Come on! Yes,you can!\N- 把他拉开,快点 - 必须说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:11.57,1:45:13.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,he can!\N他必须说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:13.07,1:45:14.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,shit!\N噢 该死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:14.50,1:45:16.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Gun! Gun! Gun!\N枪!枪!枪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:16.41,1:45:17.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Bob,don't! Put the gun down!\N鲍勃 不要 把枪放下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:17.61,1:45:20.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Bob. Bob. Put the gun down!\N鲍勃 鲍勃 把枪放下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:20.31,1:45:22.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Bob,Bob,Bob,Bob,Bob,no! No,no,no!\N鲍勃 鲍勃 鲍勃 不 不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:22.75,1:45:24.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No,no,no!\N不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:26.08,1:45:28.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.\N操
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:30.42,1:45:32.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go call a fuckin' R.A.!\N去打电话叫法医来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:32.92,1:45:35.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Our father who art in heaven,\N我们在天上的父
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:35.69,1:45:37.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,hallowed be thy name.\N愿人都尊你的名为圣,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:37.29,1:45:40.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thy kingdom come,\N愿你的国降临,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:40.80,1:45:42.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,thy will be done,\N愿你的旨意行在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:42.67,1:45:46.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,on earth as it is in heaven.\N如同行在天上。
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:46.00,1:45:48.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Give us this day\Nour daily bread,\N赐给我们日用的饮食
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:48.50,1:45:52.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and forgive us our trespasses...\N赦免我们的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:52.31,1:45:55.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,As we...\N如同 --
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:03.12,1:46:04.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,As we for...\N如同我们--
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:24.84,1:46:29.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He explain this before he ate the bullet? \N这是他吃枪子之前画的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:33.32,1:46:36.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\N我很抱歉.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:36.15,1:46:37.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you're sorry.\N抱歉个头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:37.69,1:46:40.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for the girls' parents.\N把那些抱歉的话留着跟孩子的父母说去吧.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:44.76,1:46:46.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do,Alex.\N我不知道我应该做什么 亚历克斯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:46.93,1:46:49.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore.\N我真的不知道我该怎么办.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:49.43,1:46:52.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And what's completely fucked up about all this\N事情会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:52.50,1:46:54.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,is I know you know where they are.\N是因为我知道你知道她们在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:57.11,1:46:59.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're done.\N我想我们已经完事了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:07.18,1:47:10.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the maze.\N她们在图画上这个迷宫里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:10.02,1:47:11.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you'll find them.\N那你要去哪里找她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:11.95,1:47:13.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:13.69,1:47:16.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?\N你刚说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:19.23,1:47:21.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,In the maze.\N在迷宫里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:21.36,1:47:22.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What... what... maze?\N什么....什么迷宫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:22.93,1:47:25.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?Where is the maze?\N迷宫在哪里? 迷宫在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:25.40,1:47:26.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where do I find it?\N怎么才能找到那个迷宫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:26.87,1:47:29.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex?\N亚历克斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:29.57,1:47:31.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex,Alex,listen to me.\N亚历克斯,亚历克斯? 听我说.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:31.07,1:47:33.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get you out of here,okay?\N我会让你离开这里的 好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:33.31,1:47:35.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me where the maze is.\N只要你告诉我迷宫在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:35.31,1:47:38.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.Just tell me,man.\N只要你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:38.38,1:47:41.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the maze?\N迷宫在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:41.32,1:47:43.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,tell me.\N快告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:43.55,1:47:46.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me where the maze is,okay?\N告诉我迷宫在哪,好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:48.39,1:47:50.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,don't fuck with me.\N快点 别再玩我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:50.26,1:47:52.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me now.\N你最好别再惹毛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:52.43,1:47:54.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me,God damn it!\N快说 该死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:54.26,1:47:55.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where they are!\N告诉我她们在哪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:55.57,1:47:58.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Tell me! Tell me!\N告诉我! 告诉我!告诉我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:01.60,1:48:03.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Something's gonna get to you,man.\N你这是自找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:03.51,1:48:05.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Something's gonna get to you!\N你这是自找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:05.74,1:48:07.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Something's gonna get to you!\N你自找的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:30.47,1:48:31.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!\N马上就来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:34.34,1:48:36.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?\N你有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:36.01,1:48:37.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Morning,ma'am.\N早上好 女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:37.34,1:48:40.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm Keller Dover.\N我是凯勒·多佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:40.14,1:48:45.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,my little girl was abducted with a friend.\N我女儿和她的朋友被绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:45.52,1:48:49.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?\N你想干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:49.32,1:48:51.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...\N嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:54.29,1:48:56.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess I haven't thought this through too good,huh?\N我想我...还没考虑好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:56.99,1:48:58.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I...\N我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:58.90,1:49:03.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinkin' a lot about what happened to your nephew.\N我一直在想有关你侄子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:03.03,1:49:05.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And I know I scared him\N我知道在警察局那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:05.47,1:49:07.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the other day at the police station,and... and...\N我吓着他了,而且...而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:07.74,1:49:09.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm tryin' to say is\N我想说的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:09.57,1:49:13.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel responsible for him running away.\N现在他逃跑了 我觉得我也有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:13.08,1:49:17.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna come on in?\N你想进来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:17.25,1:49:19.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N嗯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:28.92,1:49:31.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My husband and I were...\N我和我丈夫曾经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:31.93,1:49:35.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Very devout at one time.\N非常相爱.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:35.40,1:49:38.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Spent our summers driving around\N夏天时我们经常会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:38.27,1:49:41.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,in that camper with our son...\N开着那辆露营车带我们的儿子四处旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:41.00,1:49:44.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Handin' out pamphlets...\N给人们发放那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:44.54,1:49:48.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Spreadin' the good word.\N传播上帝福音的小册子.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:48.38,1:49:53.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,After our son died of cancer...\N自从我们的儿子死于癌症以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:53.28,1:49:57.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,We started seein' things differently.\N我们对很多事情的看法都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:57.22,1:50:00.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Adopting Alex helped...\N虽然收养亚历克斯帮我们走出了阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:00.12,1:50:03.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But we never got over it.\N但这件事还是很难让人释怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:03.46,1:50:07.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\N我很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:07.20,1:50:11.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You look very tired.\N你看起来很疲惫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:11.07,1:50:15.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,I don't sleep much.\N这些天我几乎都没睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:15.61,1:50:19.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I,uh...\N我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:19.44,1:50:23.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I keep dreaming about being lost in a maze.\N我总是梦见我在一个迷宫里迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:26.05,1:50:28.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\N我也很遗憾.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:28.82,1:50:32.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex never talks very much,so...\N亚历克斯不太喜欢说话 所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:32.15,1:50:34.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,When people come over here,I hardly know what to say.\N有人来这里的时候 我也不晓得该说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:34.76,1:50:36.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't talk much?\N他不爱说话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:36.66,1:50:38.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,he talks,you know.\N噢 他也不是完全不说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:38.33,1:50:40.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "good night"...that sort of thing.\N不过大都是『晚安』之类
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:40.73,1:50:43.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to get too much more than that out of him.\N除此之外也没什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:43.23,1:50:45.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He had an accident when he was little.\N他小时候发生过一次意外.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:45.84,1:50:47.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,After that,he started\N在那之后 他讲话就变得
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.64,1:50:50.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,choosing his words a little too carefully.\N非常小心翼翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:50.44,1:50:53.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What,uh,what kind of accident did he...\N是什么意外导致他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:53.14,1:50:55.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.\N噢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:55.65,1:50:57.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My husband kept snakes.\N我丈夫养蛇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:57.35,1:50:59.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that bad what happened,\N其实也不是太糟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:59.85,1:51:02.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but Alex had a fear of them and...\N可是亚历克斯很怕它们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:02.49,1:51:04.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my favorite memory.\N那是一段不太好的回忆.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:04.82,1:51:08.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It's none...none of my business.\N很抱歉 和你谈些有的没的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:08.59,1:51:10.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,it's...\N噢,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:13.13,1:51:15.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get you a cup of tea,Mr. Dover?\N我帮你倒杯茶吧 多佛先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:21.77,1:51:23.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.\N噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:23.01,1:51:24.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,I'm so sorry.\N噢 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:24.44,1:51:26.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had known about that already.\N我以为你已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:26.71,1:51:28.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I say it's better this way.\N我觉得对于那个恶毒的男人来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:28.71,1:51:30.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You know,that awful man,\N这样的结局再好不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:30.65,1:51:33.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,he would have spent years on death row\N否则他的余生恐怕也得在死囚牢房里度过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:33.28,1:51:35.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,just watchin' TV and gettin' fat.\N每天只能看看电视 越来越胖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:39.15,1:51:44.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Well,least I don't have to worry about losing you to PSP.\N起码我不用再担心你会被局里处分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:51.23,1:51:54.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,When forensics is finished with the guy's place,\N等法医清理和鉴定完那个家伙的房子后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:54.04,1:51:56.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna deploy the cadaver dogs.\N我们就得派出警犬去搜寻孩子们的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:56.24,1:52:00.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,kid,we can't always save the day.\N听着 孩子 我们不可能总是胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:00.31,1:52:04.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right? We're just cops,janitors.\N对吗? 我们只不过是警察而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:04.15,1:52:08.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So you lost this one,all right?\N这次我们已经失败了 明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:08.08,1:52:10.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Look,you want fulfillment,you need to find a girl,\N听我说 如果你想要有成就感 那就去找个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:10.92,1:52:13.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you know,start a family,have some kids.\N结婚成家 生些孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:13.26,1:52:14.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go.\N让件事过去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:44.25,1:53:45.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?\N喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:45.65,1:53:50.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,it's Rich.We found somethin'.\N我是瑞奇 我们有新发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:50.09,1:53:53.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Guys,let us have a look.\N伙计们 让我们看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:58.13,1:54:00.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Two kid-sized department store mannequins,\N两个百货商店的假人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:00.50,1:54:01.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,with their heads caved in.\N被砸烂了脑袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.96,1:54:04.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I just talked to our lab guys,\N我刚跟实验室的人通过电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:04.03,1:54:06.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and they told me that all the blood that we sampled\N他们说我们之前提取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:06.50,1:54:08.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,from the plastic containers pig's blood.\N那些塑料容器里的血样都是猪血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:08.67,1:54:11.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,All right,you guys,let's get this covered up.\N好吧 伙计们 把这些都盖上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:11.21,1:54:13.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to snow soon.Hurry up,okay?\N这里很快就要下雪了 动作快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:16.38,1:54:17.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's play-acting.\N他似乎是在玩角色扮演
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:17.81,1:54:19.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,case in point.\N我的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:19.68,1:54:21.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Except for the few items I.D.'d by the Dovers and the Birches,\N除了多佛先生和布奇先生家孩子们的衣服之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:21.68,1:54:23.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,all the kids' clothes that we found\N我们找到的其他衣服上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:23.45,1:54:24.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,still had the tags on them.\N都还挂着商店的标签
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:24.95,1:54:27.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And that maze book that we found,he made it.\N还有 那本迷宫书
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:27.02,1:54:28.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Photocopies,pictures from this book\N是他自己做的影印本
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:28.82,1:54:30.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that we found in the attic.\N原本是在阁楼上被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:30.23,1:54:32.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ex-F.B.I. Agent wrote that.\N作者是一位前联邦调查局探员
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:32.23,1:54:34.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,"Finding the Invisible Man."\N《发现隐形人》
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:34.80,1:54:37.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,it's about a theoretical suspect that he believed\N是关于一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:37.13,1:54:39.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,was responsible for a bunch of child abductions.\N儿童绑架案的嫌疑人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:39.20,1:54:40.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally discredited,I guess,\N我觉得可信度不高
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:40.74,1:54:42.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,but I read some of it.\N不过我读了一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:42.24,1:54:43.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Taylor... Taylor was abducted when he was a kid.\N泰勒 泰勒小时候也被绑架过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:43.84,1:54:45.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away after three weeks.\N不过三周后他逃出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:45.24,1:54:46.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And the captor drugged him\N绑架他的人喂他吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:46.54,1:54:48.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,on some sort of LSD/Ketamine cocktail.\N氯胺酮和迷幻剂混合出来的麻醉药
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:48.51,1:54:50.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He never remembered. They never caught the guy.\N所以他什么都不记得了 警察最终也没抓到那个罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:50.85,1:54:52.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,so...\N所以说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:52.65,1:54:54.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He read the book\N他是读了这本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:54.08,1:54:56.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and decided he was taken by the invisible man.\N决定假扮被这个隐形人抓走的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:56.52,1:54:59.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's doing his best imitation,right?\N现在他又开始模仿这个隐形人 是么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:01.19,1:55:03.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,he was doing his best imitation.\N对 他在尽力模仿这个隐形人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:03.93,1:55:06.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He killed himself last night.\N昨晚他自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:06.16,1:55:09.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How did he do that? I thought he was in custody.\N怎么会这样 我以为他还在拘留所呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:13.50,1:55:16.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:16.34,1:55:18.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Taylor drew this. \N泰勒画了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:18.41,1:55:19.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's a map to the bodies.\N这是一张藏尸地的地图.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:19.68,1:55:21.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And we found the same design on a pendant\N我们前几天在那个地下室里的尸体上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:21.61,1:55:23.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,that we pulled off that corpse the other day.\N也找到了与之相同的图案的挂坠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:23.78,1:55:25.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,There's a connection. Okay?\N这肯定有某种关联 明白么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:25.61,1:55:28.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The connection is that it's the last maze in the book.\N所谓的关联就是 这是这本书里的最后一个迷宫图
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:28.85,1:55:31.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I did it. It's unsolvable.There's no way out.\N我试解了一下 是个没有出口的迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:31.62,1:55:34.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Your corpse is another wannabe who read the book.\N那具尸体可能是这本书的另外一个模仿者
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:34.59,1:55:36.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying to me,Rich?\N你什么意思 瑞奇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:36.06,1:55:38.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying to me? What are you saying?\N你想说什么? 你想表达什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:38.03,1:55:39.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That... that...that this guy is a fake?\N你想说这人只是个假货?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:39.73,1:55:41.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that the girls...\N你想说那些女孩....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:41.13,1:55:42.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,the girls are still out there somewhere?\N那些女孩仍然还在其它什么地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:42.87,1:55:44.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How did Bob Taylor get those clothes?\N那鲍勃·泰勒是怎么拿到那些衣服的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:44.47,1:55:46.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How did... how did the parents...\N为什么...她们的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:46.37,1:55:49.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Positively I.D.Those clothes?!\N能指认出那些衣服?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:49.77,1:55:54.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That I can't reconcile.\N这个 我也解释不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:54.31,1:55:55.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reconcile that?\N你解释不了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:55.81,1:55:58.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep knockin' on doors,look in the windows.\N就去继续敲门调查就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:58.48,1:56:01.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,why is that there? Bag that.\N为什么那玩意还在哪里? 快装起来..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:01.05,1:56:02.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Will do,sir. Right away.\N好的长官 马上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:29.80,1:57:31.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?\N你好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:33.98,1:57:37.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Um,yeah. This is she.\N对 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:41.02,1:57:42.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:45.02,1:57:46.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my God!\N噢 上帝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:46.36,1:57:49.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,wait. Is she...?\N噢,等等,她是不是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:49.89,1:57:53.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Ralph! Keller!\N拉尔夫 凯勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:08.71,1:58:11.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keller! We need to go to the hospital!\N凯勒! 我们得去医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:11.01,1:58:12.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They found joy,but not Anna! What?\N她们找到乔伊了,但是没找到安娜. 什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:12.92,1:58:14.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't find Anna!\N她们没有找到安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:14.52,1:58:17.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll know where Anna is! Please,we have to go!\N也许她会知道安娜在哪 ! 我们现在过去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:17.05,1:58:19.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keller!\N凯勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:21.39,1:58:24.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza's not picking up.\N伊莱扎不接电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:24.09,1:58:25.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You should text her.\N你应该发短信给她.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:25.79,1:58:29.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N我发了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:35.47,1:58:36.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody gets beyond this point.\N你们不能过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:36.97,1:58:38.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.\N别碰我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:38.37,1:58:39.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Wait a minute...\N女士 请等一下!--
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:39.78,1:58:41.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.\N没事的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:41.04,1:58:42.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy.\N南茜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.24,1:58:44.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Grace.\N格蕾丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:44.11,1:58:46.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find Anna. I know they will.\N- 他们会找到安娜的,- 会的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:46.15,1:58:47.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know they will.\N我知道他们会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:47.55,1:58:49.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know.How is she?\N我知道. 她怎么样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:49.32,1:58:51.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Is she awake?\N她醒着吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.39,1:58:53.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy,were you far from our street?\N乔伊 你之前在什么地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:53.82,1:58:56.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How far from the street were you,Joy?\N离这里远吗,乔伊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:56.43,1:58:57.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy?\N乔伊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:57.66,1:58:59.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be doing this now.\N你现在不能问她问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:59.33,1:59:01.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,How long did it take you to get there?\N那里离我们街区多远?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:01.43,1:59:03.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me ask a question! Please. Keller!\N- 就让我问这一个问题就好 求你了 - 凯勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:03.47,1:59:04.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The detective will be back in just a minute.\N警探马上就会回来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:04.63,1:59:05.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You need to wait.\N你就等一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:05.63,1:59:07.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She's been drugged.\N她被麻醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:07.00,1:59:08.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy.\N乔伊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:08.60,1:59:09.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart...\N宝贝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:09.91,1:59:14.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just let us know she's alive,okay?\N告诉我们她是不是还活着 好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:14.28,1:59:15.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can you just nod your head,baby?\N宝贝 你可以点一下头吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:15.58,1:59:18.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just nod your head? Baby?\N就点一下头 好吗宝贝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:18.75,1:59:20.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us a nod?\N你可以点一下头吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:20.18,1:59:22.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can you nod your head for us,please? Joy?\N可以点一下头吗?求你了,乔伊.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:32.69,1:59:36.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Joy?\N乔伊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:06.50,2:00:10.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You were there.\N你当时也在那里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:10.80,2:00:13.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What? I was... I was where?\N什么？我在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:13.47,2:00:16.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It put tape on our mouths.\N他们用胶带把她的嘴封上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:16.97,2:00:18.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh.\N嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:18.34,2:00:23.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.It's okay,baby.\N没事 宝贝 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:23.48,2:00:25.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's okay.\N没事的,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:25.35,2:00:28.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and daddy are here now,okay?\N爸爸妈妈都在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:28.42,2:00:29.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right.\N你还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:29.75,2:00:32.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. You're all right now.\N抱歉 你现在没事了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:32.15,2:00:34.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I said nobody's allowed in that room but her family.\N我说过除了她的家人谁都不能进病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:34.42,2:00:36.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where you goin'?\N嘿 你要去哪里??
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:36.73,2:00:38.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keller?\N凯勒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:38.09,2:00:39.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's he goin'?\N嘿 他要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:39.49,2:00:41.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Hey!\N- 我不知道. - 嘿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:41.83,2:00:43.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Call downstairs. Don't let him go.\N叫楼下的人注意 别让他跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:43.73,2:00:45.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Block off the exits.\N站住！ 堵住出口.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:45.90,2:00:49.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\N嘿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:50.57,2:00:52.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that car! Get his truck!\N截住那辆车 截住他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:52.11,2:00:55.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Hey! Hey!\N别跑,嘿! 嘿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:14.53,2:01:18.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you,you fucker.\N你跑不掉的 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:18.77,2:01:21.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know where you're goin'.\N我知道你要去哪 .
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:21.40,2:01:23.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know where you're goin'.\N我知道你要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:41.52,2:02:43.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello again.\N你好.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:43.39,2:02:48.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I was hoping you'd,uh,you'd let me do some penance.\N我希望你...能让我做点什么 弥补我的过错
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:48.72,2:02:51.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,For what?\N为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:51.46,2:02:55.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,For scaring you the other day at the,uh,the police station.\N之前在警察局的时候我吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:55.46,2:02:58.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You already apologized for that.\N你已经道过歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:58.17,2:03:00.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I was... you know,I thought maybe you,uh...\N我知道 我只是觉得...也许...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:00.90,2:03:03.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You could use some,uh,help around the...\N也许我可以帮你做点什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:03.17,2:03:05.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,you know,I noticed your door here needs fixing,\N我注意到你的门需要修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:05.67,2:03:07.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,so I brought my tools and,uh...\N所以我带来了工具 而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:07.51,2:03:09.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.\N噢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:09.18,2:03:11.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\N我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:13.68,2:03:18.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I burned myself.Feel a little icky today.\N我把自己烫伤了. 今天感觉不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:18.05,2:03:22.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you want to talk some more.\N我很高兴你还想要谈谈这事
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:22.02,2:03:23.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No need to make excuses.\N不过也用不着找什么借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:23.83,2:03:26.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You come on in and make me a cup of tea.\N你进来吧 顺便帮我泡杯茶.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:35.54,2:03:38.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.\N请进.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:57.36,2:04:01.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to have to hurt you.\N我不想伤害你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:01.96,2:04:04.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know they were here.\N我知道她们在这里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:04.93,2:04:10.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on your head and turn around.\N把手举起来 转过身来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:10.74,2:04:12.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.\N照我说的做.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:15.58,2:04:17.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna go.\N我这就走.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:17.28,2:04:19.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that bag.\N别碰那个包
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:19.55,2:04:22.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on your head.\N把手放到头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:26.62,2:04:29.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here to this counter.\N走到台子这来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:29.09,2:04:30.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!\N快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:38.60,2:04:42.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Top drawer.\N最上边的抽屉
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:42.10,2:04:44.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.\N打开它
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:53.31,2:04:56.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put them on.\N自己戴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:04.59,2:05:07.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know me,Mr. Dover.\N你不了解我 多佛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:07.70,2:05:12.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But believe me when I tell you,I won't let you go.\N但是相信我 我不会放你走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:19.84,2:05:22.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to drink all of it.\N不用全喝完
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:22.54,2:05:27.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,About a third should do for a man your size.\N像你这样的体格 三分之一差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:27.15,2:05:29.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Something to make you more manageable.\N那会让你变得老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:29.95,2:05:31.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.\N想都别想
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:31.65,2:05:32.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it,Mr. Dover,\N喝掉它 多佛先生.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:32.95,2:05:35.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll kill you right here in my kitchen\N要不我只好在厨房动手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:35.16,2:05:36.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and bring your daughter in here\N然后我会把你女儿带来这里,
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:36.63,2:05:38.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and have her scrub your brains off the floor...\N让她来把地板上的你的脑浆擦干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:38.03,2:05:39.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?\N她在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:42.40,2:05:44.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Drink.\N快喝.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:44.20,2:05:45.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me see her.\N让我见见她.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:45.97,2:05:48.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see her? Yes!\N- 你想要见她? - 对
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:48.37,2:05:51.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's your ticket to your daughter right there.\N把那个喝了 我就带你去见女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:01.88,2:06:04.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,A little more,Mr. Dover.\N再多喝一点 多佛先生.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:04.15,2:06:06.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Little more.\N再多一点.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:11.49,2:06:13.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Good,isn't it?\N味道不错,不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:13.23,2:06:17.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's my darlin' husband's recipe.\N那可是我亲爱的丈夫的秘方.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:24.24,2:06:26.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now go on out back.\N现在我们到后院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:26.58,2:06:29.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see her.\N让我见她.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:32.58,2:06:36.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Take it out of your pocket.\N把手机从你的口袋里拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:38.69,2:06:40.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in the sink.\N扔进水槽里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:42.72,2:06:45.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in the disposal.\N扔到污水处理槽里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:53.20,2:06:55.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put your car keys on the table.\N把你的车钥匙放在桌子上.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:58.47,2:07:01.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Put your car keys on the table.\N把你的车钥匙放在桌子上.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:01.88,2:07:05.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\N这就对了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:05.15,2:07:07.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Over to the trans am over there.\N那边 那辆通用汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:07.25,2:07:08.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The car over there.\N那边那辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:08.75,2:07:11.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,move it. Get over there.\N快走 到那边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:18.83,2:07:22.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,The look on your face.\N你脸上的表情.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:22.23,2:07:24.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,My husband used to have the very same look...\N和我丈夫当时的表情太相像了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:24.97,2:07:26.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Till we took Alex.\N直到我们抓走了亚历克斯.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:26.43,2:07:29.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first kid we ever took.\N他是我们抓走的第一个孩子.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:29.14,2:07:30.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Jimmy.\N他的本名叫吉米.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:30.64,2:07:33.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Or Barry.\N或者巴瑞?.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:33.31,2:07:35.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Can't remember. Doubt he can,either.\N我不记得了 我怀疑连他自己也不记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:35.34,2:07:37.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,So many names.\N名字太多了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:37.11,2:07:39.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot all about Bobby Taylor\N我几乎都已经忘记鲍勃·泰勒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:39.68,2:07:43.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,till I read about him in the paper.\N直到我在报纸上发现了他的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:43.08,2:07:46.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the driver's seat.\N坐到驾驶座上
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:55.33,2:07:58.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door and get in the car.\N打开车门 进去车里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:12.31,2:08:18.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Making children disappear is the war we wage with God.\N让孩子们一个个消失 就是我们向上帝宣战的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:18.69,2:08:21.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Makes people lose their faith.\N让人失去他们的信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:21.82,2:08:25.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Turns them into demons like you.\N让他们变成像你一样的恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:25.13,2:08:30.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Had to slow down since my husband disappeared.\N自从我丈夫失踪以后 我不得不放慢速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:30.47,2:08:33.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I do what I can.\N但是我依然在尽我所能
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:33.70,2:08:35.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Start the car.\N点火
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:35.90,2:08:38.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Start the car.\N点火
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:43.01,2:08:45.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Keep tryin'.\N继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:50.32,2:08:53.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Back up. Slowly.\N倒车 慢点.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:56.86,2:09:01.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Back up.\N倒车.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:02.70,2:09:04.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\N快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:07.67,2:09:09.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.\N停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:09.40,2:09:11.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it off.\N熄火
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:11.74,2:09:13.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it off!\N熄火!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:15.04,2:09:17.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.\N下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:25.42,2:09:27.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Think you should know.\N我想告诉你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:27.39,2:09:30.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Alex never laid a hand on those girls.\N亚历克斯从来没有碰过那些女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:30.76,2:09:33.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just wanted to take 'em for a ride in the camper.\N他只是想要带她们去兜风而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:33.96,2:09:36.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who decided they should stay.\N是我决定要把她们关在房子里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:39.07,2:09:42.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.\N看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:42.40,2:09:44.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your daughter's under there.\N也许你女儿就在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:44.91,2:09:47.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You never know.\N谁知道呢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:49.21,2:09:51.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna.\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:51.05,2:09:53.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:53.78,2:09:55.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:58.15,2:10:00.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna. Anna!\N安娜!安娜!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:00.89,2:10:02.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:02.06,2:10:03.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?!\N安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:03.63,2:10:05.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I had the girls down there\N警察过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:05.63,2:10:08.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when the police came pokin' around.\N我就让那些女孩待在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:08.50,2:10:11.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Should have left 'em down there.\N我该让她们一直待在那儿的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:11.17,2:10:13.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I was so lonely without Alex.\N但亚历克斯不在的时候 我觉得非常孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:16.40,2:10:17.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Now get in there.\N现在进去那里.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:17.84,2:10:19.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:19.91,2:10:21.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.\N进去.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:24.31,2:10:28.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to get in there,you're gonna have to shoot me.\N除非你给我来上一枪 不然我不会进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:28.15,2:10:31.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna get in there just 'cause you asked.\N凭什么你让我进去我就进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:41.86,2:10:46.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Get in there.\N快点 进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:51.10,2:10:53.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's right.\N很好 这就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:13.33,2:11:16.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourself a tourniquet.\N给你自己弄个止血带吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:16.53,2:11:19.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just might last 24 hours.\N你大概还能撑个24小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:24.17,2:11:26.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love for you to still be alive\N我希望你能活到
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:26.21,2:11:28.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,when I dump your daughter's body down there.\N我把你女儿的尸体扔进去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:33.85,2:11:36.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No,wait,wait,wait!\N等等!不 等等 等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:36.02,2:11:37.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!\N等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:39.49,2:11:41.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:41.42,2:11:43.49,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:06.21,2:12:07.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:07.85,2:12:09.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to go over to Holly Jones.\N你去通知下赫莉·琼斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:09.58,2:12:10.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to be notified.\N关于他侄子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:10.85,2:12:12.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No. I need to find Dover.\N我需要你帮我找到多佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:12.22,2:12:14.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You're done with Dover,okay? Please?\N你不要再操心多佛了 求你了行么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:14.19,2:12:16.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go to Holly Jones?\N你想让我去找赫莉·琼斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:16.09,2:12:19.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go to holly Jones' and notify her,please.\N我想让你去通知一下赫莉·琼斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:31.97,2:12:35.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,God.\N噢 上帝啊.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:48.28,2:13:49.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Almighty God...\N全知全能的主...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:49.85,2:13:52.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Protect my girl.\N求您保护我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:05.23,2:15:07.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Jones?\N琼斯女士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:19.04,2:15:20.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Jones?\N琼斯女士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:52.17,2:16:54.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your hands right now.\N马上举起手来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:54.07,2:16:57.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move and show me your fuckin' hands right now.\N别动 马上把你的手给我举起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:57.81,2:17:00.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Right now!\N别动!听见没有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:00.01,2:17:01.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your fuckin' hands.\N把手举起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:01.34,2:17:02.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do not move and show me your hands.\N别动 举起手来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:02.98,2:17:04.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure they cremate me.\N记得让他们火化我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:04.81,2:17:08.31,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I sure as hell don't want to be buried in some box.\N我可不想躺在什么木头箱子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:08.32,2:17:09.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands! Right now!\N两只手 快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:09.68,2:17:11.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!\N快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:12.69,2:17:13.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!\N操!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:24.23,2:17:26.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna.\N安娜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:26.57,2:17:29.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my God.\N噢,天哪.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:45.45,2:17:48.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,God.\N噢,天哪.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:48.96,2:17:51.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anna.\N安娜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:06.71,2:18:09.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,shit.\N该死.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:24.43,2:18:29.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on. Anna. Anna. Come on.\N安娜 安娜 坚持住 坚持住
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:33.33,2:18:37.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me,Anna.Anna,stay with me,huh?\N别睡着 安娜 不要睡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:37.07,2:18:39.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me,Anna!\N坚持住 安娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:46.31,2:18:48.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me,Anna! It's all right!\N坚持住 安娜! 已经没事了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:48.75,2:18:50.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Come on!\N没事了! 坚持住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:50.58,2:18:52.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Go,move,move,move,move!\N快点 快点 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:01.49,2:19:03.50,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die,don't die.\N不要死 不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:30.69,2:19:32.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay,it's okay.\N到了 到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:32.99,2:19:35.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Honey. You're okay.\N宝贝 你不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:35.70,2:19:37.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:37.13,2:19:38.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.\N嘿.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:38.37,2:19:41.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Help!\N嘿！来人帮忙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:41.30,2:19:44.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Help!\N医生！医生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:44.07,2:19:45.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N医生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:45.34,2:19:47.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Help!\N医生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:08.19,2:20:10.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,detective Loki?\N洛奇警探?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:12.33,2:20:15.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we're not intruding.\N希望我们没有打扰到你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:15.60,2:20:17.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:21.78,2:20:25.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing real good.\N她恢复得很不错.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:25.11,2:20:27.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna be up and around in a few days,\N过几天就可以走路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:27.85,2:20:29.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you,buddy?\N是不是 宝贝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:29.72,2:20:33.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She just wanted to come and say thank you and hi to her hero.\N她想要过来跟她的英雄打个招呼 还有谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:37.09,2:20:39.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.\N你好.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:47.43,2:20:50.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,would you mind giving me a minute?\N介意我单独和他谈谈么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:50.70,2:20:53.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you.\N- 行 - 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:53.27,2:20:55.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Say Goodbye,joy. Bye.\N- 乔伊 说再见 - 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:55.28,2:20:56.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be out in a minute.All right?\N我很快出来 好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:56.58,2:20:57.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Say goodbye,Anna.\N说再见 安娜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:23.14,2:21:26.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She found her whistle?\N她找到她的口哨了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:26.07,2:21:28.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,no.\N噢 不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:28.11,2:21:31.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,She keeps insisting that Joy helped her find it\N她一直坚持说  口哨是感恩节那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:31.75,2:21:34.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,on Thanksgiving before they were taken.\N她们被带走前 乔伊帮她找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:34.82,2:21:37.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she's just confused.\N可是我觉得她的脑袋还有点糊涂.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:37.45,2:21:39.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I got her a new one.\N是我给她买了只新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:56.30,2:21:59.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't contacted me.\N他还没有跟我联系过.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:01.88,2:22:03.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't...\N我知道你不会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:03.94,2:22:08.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I know you probably don't believe that,but he hasn't.\N我知道你可能不相信我 但他真的没有联络过我.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:13.72,2:22:17.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I-I believe you.\N我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:23.83,2:22:26.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're gonna find him?\N你觉得你能找到他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:30.07,2:22:32.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:32.71,2:22:35.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll go to jail.\N他会进监狱么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:35.38,2:22:39.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.\N也许.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:42.72,2:22:45.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...\N总之...
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:45.22,2:22:47.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.\N谢谢你所做的一切.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:50.26,2:22:54.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,God.\N噢 天哪.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:03.70,2:23:05.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,I miss him.\N我真的很想他
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:09.41,2:23:14.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He... He did what he had to do to find Anna,\N他那么做只是为了找到安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:14.11,2:23:16.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,and I thank God for that.\N感谢上帝能保佑他.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:25.63,2:23:28.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good man.\N他是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:36.60,2:23:39.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.\N拜拜.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:03.93,2:24:05.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.Let's pack it up.\N就这样吧 收工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:12.81,2:24:15.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,You all done for the night?\N今晚的活都干完了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:15.58,2:24:17.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,the ground's frozen solid.\N对 地面都已经冻住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:17.61,2:24:20.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna take weeks to excavate the entire property.\N要把这片地方都挖开 起码得一个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:20.15,2:24:22.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Just found some dead snakes and shit.\N目前为止我们只找到了一些死蛇什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:24.62,2:24:28.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Pray for the best,prepare for the worst,yeah?\N祈求最好的结果 做好最坏的打算 对吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:28.02,2:24:31.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Night.\N晚安.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:32.83,2:24:36.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Night.\N晚安.
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:36.10,2:24:37.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Shut her down.\N把机器关了吧


